(1, 'tt4566516', '1', 'Pilot, Part 1', 'MV5BMTUwMzQxOTc5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTI1MzU1NzE@', 'Time-traveling rogue, Rip Hunter, has to recruit a rag-tag team of heroes and villains to help prevent an apocalypse that could impact not only Earth, but all of time.', 1, 1, '21 Jan. 2016'),
