(158, 'tt4006572', '5', 'Canaries', 'MV5BMTU3NTYwNDQxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjE1OTkzNDE@', 'Oliver struggles to adjust to the changes that have taken place within Team Arrow; Laurel ignores Oliver and pursues Vertigo - who injects her with the drug; Thea receives a surprise visitor.', 3, 13, '11 Feb. 2015'),
(159, 'tt4006600', '5', 'The Return', 'MV5BMjE5NDI5NzE4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzM2NDQ0NDE@', 'Malcolm puts Oliver and Thea in a dangerous situation that lands them on Lian Yu with Oliver''s former enemy, Deathstroke. A flashback reveals when Oliver and Maseo returned to Starling City to retrieve the Omega bio weapon, and despite being under strict ', 3, 14, '18 Feb. 2015'),
(160, 'tt4006588', '5', 'Nanda Parbat', 'MV5BMTQ2NjA0MDg2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTM4NDQ2NDE@', 'Malcolm is captured by Ra''s al Ghul and taken to Nanda Parbat. Because of his love for Thea, Oliver considers saving Merlyn. Ray is obsessed with finishing his Atom suit so he can save the city but Felicity fears he is heading down the same path as Oliver', 3, 15, '25 Feb. 2015'),
(161, 'tt4006594', '5', 'The Offer', 'MV5BNzk5OTE3MDY3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA2NTM4NDE@', 'Oliver thinks about the offer Ra''s Al Ghul gave him, but to do so theres a catch.', 3, 16, '18 Mar. 2015'),
(162, 'tt4006606', '5', 'Suicidal Tendencies', 'MV5BMTg0Nzg3Nzc1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQzNTM4NDE@', 'It''s celebration time as Diggle and Lyla get married. However, Deadshot interrupts their honeymoon and tells them the Suicide Squad has been given a new mission - rescue United States Senator Joseph Cray from a hostage situation in the Republic of Kasnia.', 3, 17, '25 Mar. 2015'),
(163, 'tt4006596', '5', 'Public Enemy', 'MV5BNjc4MzU5NzY5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTgzNzIxNTE@', 'During an attack on the mayor''s office, Ray is critically injured. Felicity is pleasantly surprised when her mother, Donna Smoak, shows up at the hospital to offer her support. With the SCPD out in full force looking for the assailant, Oliver and his team', 3, 18, '1 Apr. 2015'),
(164, 'tt4006602', '5', 'Broken Arrow', 'MV5BMTU4Mjk3MDQ3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQ5NDUzNTE@', 'Jake Simmons, a metahuman from Central City, terrorizes the Starling City. Quentin Lance''s mission bounds Oliver Queen to ask Ray (Atom) for help.', 3, 19, '15 Apr. 2015'),
(165, 'tt4006584', '5', 'The Fallen', 'MV5BMTY2MDYyNjk1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTI1MzI0NTE@', 'Ra''s al Ghul finally makes Oliver an offer he can''t refuse. The team joins Oliver on his journey to Nanda Parbat where a heartbroken Felicity decides to take matters into her own hands.', 3, 20, '22 Apr. 2015'),
(166, 'tt4006598', '5', 'Al Sah-Him', 'MV5BMTYzNTEwNDYxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTk3MjM1NTE@', 'Oliver goes through a transformation; Laurel asks Felicity and Diggle to help Nyssa face the League of Assassins.', 3, 21, '29 Apr. 2015'),
(167, 'tt4006590', '5', 'This Is Your Sword', 'MV5BMTQ5MTQzNzU0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODYxMTQ2NTE@', 'Oliver must complete two final tasks before becoming the next Ra''s al Ghul; Nyssa is threatened; Malcolm makes an offer to the team; Thea visits Roy.', 3, 22, '6 May 2015'),
(168, 'tt4006604', '5', 'My Name Is Oliver Queen', 'MV5BMTk4MDIwNzY0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTI3Nzg2NTE@', 'Ra''s al Ghul sets his plan in motion, putting everyone in danger; Oliver must decide if he is strong enough to handle his new role - and what it will mean for his team and his soul.', 3, 23, '13 May 2015'),
(169, 'tt4345922', '5', 'Green Arrow', 'MV5BMTU4ODkzNTA4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTYzNzMyNjE@', 'A new enemy lures Oliver Queen back to Starling City and forces him to put on the hood once more.', 4, 1, '7 Oct. 2015'),
(170, 'tt4765782', '5', 'The Candidate', 'MV5BMjMzMzkyMzEwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQwMDMwNzE@', 'Oliver and Thea are concerned when a family friend plans to run for mayor; Thea starts to exhibit side effects from the Lazarus Pit; Felicity asks an employee for help with a business decision.', 4, 2, '14 Oct. 2015'),
(171, 'tt4846212', '5', 'Restoration', 'MV5BMjI4NjY5MDMxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTA0NzgwNzE@', 'The growing tension between Oliver and Diggle puts both their lives at risk when they go after Damien Darhk and a H.I.V.E. deployed meta-human. Meanwhile, Laurel talks Thea into returning to Nanda Parbat to ask her father to put Sara into the Lazarus Pit.', 4, 3, '21 Oct. 2015'),
(172, 'tt4854000', '5', 'Beyond Redemption', 'MV5BMTUzNTU3OTQyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY5NTQxNzE@', 'Laurel must deal with the repercussions of taking Sara to Nanda Parbat. Meanwhile, Oliver asks Captain Lance for a favor and while he''s not surprised at the response, he is surprised at what he finds out next.', 4, 4, '28 Oct. 2015'),
(173, 'tt4859064', '5', 'Haunted', 'MV5BNTM3OTc5NTk5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzgwMzkxNzE@', 'Oliver calls in a favor from old friend John Constantine when Sara takes a turn for the worse.', 4, 5, '4 Nov. 2015'),
(174, 'tt4859298', '5', 'Lost Souls', 'MV5BMjQyMDYwMDI3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDIzMTMyNzE@', 'Felicity is frantic when she learns that Ray is alive and being held by Damien Darhk. Felicity''s guilt over not finding Ray sooner causes tension between her and Oliver.', 4, 6, '11 Nov. 2015'),
(175, 'tt4859296', '5', 'Brotherhood', 'MV5BMTY2NjY1Mjg4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjMwODUyNzE@', 'A shocking revelation complicates the battle between Team Arrow and Damien Darhk; Thea loses control in front of Alex.', 4, 7, '18 Nov. 2015'),
(176, 'tt4859300', '5', 'Legends of Yesterday', 'MV5BMzU2MTAwODM1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA3ODMzNzE@', 'Oliver and Barry hide Kendra and Carter in a remote location while they try to figure out how to defeat Vandal Savage; Felicity, Thea, Diggle and Laurel work to come up with a weapon to destroy Vandal.', 4, 8, '2 Dec. 2015'),
(177, 'tt4859302', '5', 'Dark Waters', 'MV5BMjA5ODMyMDM5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTMzNjQ0NzE@', 'Oliver moves against HIVE; Malcolm goes to see Thea, leaving her with a warning; Damien Darhk retaliates at Oliver''s holiday party.', 4, 9, '9 Dec. 2015'),
(178, 'tt4862532', '5', 'Blood Debts', 'MV5BMTY5ODIwMjM4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjA5NTg3NzE@', 'Oliver must deal with the devastating consequences of Darhk''s last attack. Seeking revenge, Oliver goes on a brutal manhunt looking for Dahrk.', 4, 10, '20 Jan. 2016'),
(179, 'tt4862534', '5', 'A.W.O.L.', 'MV5BODYxNTY5MDgxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTA5ODE4NzE@', 'An agent of Shadowspire who was an enemy from Diggle and Andy''s wartime past shows up to Star City. Diggle must learn to trust Andy but he got more than he wanted about their shared time from war. Oliver however must learn a new way of life when Felicity ', 4, 11, '27 Jan. 2016'),
