(368, 'tt0751141', '10', 'Ice', 'MV5BMjE2MTA4MTc2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ0Nzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully are sent to investigate when a team of geophysicists stationed at a remote Alaskan outpost are killed by a parasitic alien life form.', 1, 8, '5 Nov. 1993'),
(369, 'tt0751207', '10', 'Space', 'MV5BMjA5NDgxMTIzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzY1Nzc3MjE@', 'When a space shuttle mission is sabotaged, Mulder suspects it may be the work an alien spirit that inhabits the body of a former Gemini astronaut.', 1, 9, '12 Nov. 1993'),
(370, 'tt0751120', '10', 'Fallen Angel', 'MV5BMTg3MzA2MDg0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzgzNzc3MjE@', 'The future of the X-Files project is jeopardized after Mulder secretly infiltrates the government cover-up of a UFO crash.', 1, 10, '19 Nov. 1993'),
