(400, 'tt0751093', '10', 'Colony', 'MV5BMTg1MjUyMjc5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDYzNzc3MjE@', 'When someone sends Mulder and Scully obituaries showing three separate but identical men apparently having died, the agents investigate, but things take an unexpected turn when Mulder receives a call from his father.', 2, 16, '10 Feb. 1995'),
