(554, 'tt0751253', '10', 'Underneath', 'MV5BNDc4MjM4NzgzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDg1Nzc3MjE@', 'After thirteen years in prison, a man named Fassl is released and cleared of murder charges when DNA evidence proves he had nothing to do with the murder of an entire family though he was present on the scene. Doggett, who made the arrest, refuses to acce', 9, 12, '31 Mar. 2002'),
(555, 'tt0751142', '10', 'Improbable', 'MV5BMTg5ODg1MjI1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM0Nzc3MjE@', 'Reyes, Doggett, and Scully are pulled into a bizarre serial murder case involving the number ''3'', numerology on a whole, and an eccentric man who likes to play checkers.', 9, 13, '7 Apr. 2002'),
(556, 'tt0751198', '10', 'Scary Monsters', 'MV5BNjIzMzY3NDk4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY1Nzc3MjE@', 'Reyes and Doggett, with the aid of a young Mulder-worshiping FBI agent, investigate a father who is exhibiting bizarre behavior regarding his son who he has kept hidden from the outside world.', 9, 14, '14 Apr. 2002'),
(557, 'tt0751148', '10', 'Jump the Shark', 'MV5BMTQyNjQ4NDYzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQ0Nzc3MjE@', 'The Lone Gunmen, with the (unwanted) aide of Morris Fletcher, must stop a destructive virus from entering the populace.', 9, 15, '21 Apr. 2002'),
(558, 'tt0751261', '10', 'William', 'MV5BMTg3NTA2NTA2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODE2Nzc3MjE@', 'A disfigured man attacks Doggett trying to retrieve X-Files for Mulder...but he might be Mulder himself.', 9, 16, '28 Apr. 2002'),
(559, 'tt0751189', '10', 'Release', 'MV5BMTEyODIyMjIxNjVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDUxNTc3NzIx', 'A Frank Black-esque cadet in Scully''s class directs Doggett to a current murder case that may have something to do with a case that went unsolved 9 years prior...the murder of his young son.', 9, 17, '5 May 2002'),
(560, 'tt0751209', '10', 'Sunshine Days', 'MV5BMjc1MzYwNTAwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzc1Nzc3MjE@', 'Reyes and Doggett investigate two murders revolving around a house that is, at some points in time, identical to the Brady Bunch house.', 9, 18, '12 May 2002'),
(561, 'tt0408347', '10', 'The Truth: Parts 1 & 2', 'MV5BMjA0NzQ3MzQ1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzgyNjg3MjE@', 'Mulder''s return leads to his being tried before a military tribunal that seeks to justify and prove the very existence of an alien conspiracy -- and the X-Files.', 9, 19, '19 May 2002');
