(563, 'tt4549948', '10', 'Founder''s Mutation', 'MV5BMTk3MzczMDQ3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjEzNzY3NzE@', 'A scientist working for the DOD commits suicide. Mulder and Scully start an investigation only to discover a secret mutation experiment.', 10, 2, '25 Jan. 2016'),
