(581, 'tt1589921', '12', 'Days Gone Bye', 'MV5BMTYwMzIwODM3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjE3MDQwNA@@', 'After being shot, Deputy Sheriff Rick Grimes awakes to find the world overrun by the undead.', 1, 1, '31 Oct. 2010'),
(582, 'tt1628064', '12', 'Guts', 'MV5BMTgxNDQzNjQ2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODg2MDQwNA@@', 'Rick finds himself trapped with a group of survivors inside a department store that is surrounded by walkers.', 1, 2, '7 Nov. 2010'),
(583, 'tt1628065', '12', 'Tell It to the Frogs', 'MV5BMTgyOTIwNDg2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzA1NzkwNA@@', 'Rick is reunited with Lori and Carl but soon decides - along with some of the other survivors - to return to the rooftop and rescue Merle. Meanwhile, tensions run high between the other survivors at the camp.', 1, 3, '14 Nov. 2010'),
(584, 'tt1628066', '12', 'Vatos', 'MV5BMTQxMzM0NzEyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTE5MjIxNA@@', 'Rick, Glenn, Daryl and T-Dog come across a group of seemingly hostile survivors whilst searching for Merle. Back at camp, Jim begins behaving erratically.', 1, 4, '21 Nov. 2010'),
(585, 'tt1628067', '12', 'Wildfire', 'MV5BMzc2OTI1Mzg0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjc3NDUyMjE@', 'After the attack on the camp, Rick leads the survivors to the C.D.C., in the hope that they can cure an infected Jim.', 1, 5, '28 Nov. 2010'),
(586, 'tt1628068', '12', 'TS-19', 'MV5BMTg0MzI4ODU0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTYxNzYxNA@@', 'The survivors gain access to the C.D.C. in the hope of a safe haven.', 1, 6, '5 Dec. 2010'),
(587, 'tt1790548', '12', 'What Lies Ahead', 'MV5BODI0NDQ1NjMyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjk0MDgyNg@@', 'The group''s plan to head for Fort Benning is put on hold when Sophia goes missing.', 2, 1, '16 Oct. 2011'),
(588, 'tt1804266', '12', 'Bloodletting', 'MV5BMTM1OTc1Nzk4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDgwNDQ5Ng@@', 'After Carl is accidentally shot, the group are brought to a family living on a nearby farm. Shane makes a dangerous trip in search of medical supplies.', 2, 2, '23 Oct. 2011'),
(589, 'tt1804267', '12', 'Save the Last One', 'MV5BNzM3OTA5NjM0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTQ0Njc5Ng@@', 'As Carl''s condition continues to deteriorate, Shane and Otis try to dodge the walkers as they head back to the farm.', 2, 3, '30 Oct. 2011'),
(590, 'tt1804268', '12', 'Cherokee Rose', 'MV5BNzA4NDkxNTgxMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzIzOTEwNw@@', 'With Carl recovering, the group puts their focus on finding Sophia. Glenn and Maggie go for a trip to find supplies.', 2, 4, '6 Nov. 2011'),
(591, 'tt1804269', '12', 'Chupacabra', 'MV5BNjUwMmExZDgtMTIzZS00YzYwLWIyMTktMzAxZGIxMzkzNDBkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzQ0MDAwODE@', 'Daryl becomes injured and stranded in the middle of the woods whilst searching for Sophia. Shane urges Rick to call off the search party. Hershel remains wary of the group.', 2, 5, '13 Nov. 2011'),
(592, 'tt1804270', '12', 'Secrets', 'MV5BMTM3OTkyMDYwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjUwMDYwNw@@', 'Dale confronts Hershel after Glenn tells him about the walkers in the barn. Meanwhile, Lori struggles to come to terms with her pregnancy, and Shane tries to teach Andrea how to use weapons.', 2, 6, '20 Nov. 2011'),
(593, 'tt1804271', '12', 'Pretty Much Dead Already', 'MV5BMjI3NTIyNTExN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTMzNzkwNw@@', 'Glenn tells the rest of the group about the walkers in the barn, dividing them on what to do. Meanwhile, Hershel sets a deadline for the group to leave, unless Rick does a difficult task.', 2, 7, '27 Nov. 2011'),
(594, 'tt1804272', '12', 'Nebraska', 'MV5BODczMjM3ODIzNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjMyNDEzNw@@', 'In the aftermath of the barn incident; the group bury loved ones, Beth falls into shock, and Rick and Glenn head out to find Hershel when he disappears.', 2, 8, '12 Feb. 2012'),
(595, 'tt1804273', '12', 'Triggerfinger', 'MV5BMTA3Mzg0ODc3MjZeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDkzNTI0NDc@', 'Rick, Glenn and Hershel come under enemy fire after their encounter with Dave and Tony. Meanwhile, Shane goes after Lori when everyone realizes she is missing.', 2, 9, '19 Feb. 2012'),
(596, 'tt1804262', '12', '18 Miles Out', 'MV5BMTM3MDIxNTk3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzU1MjQ0Nw@@', 'Rick and Shane argue over what to do with Randall. Back at the farm, Lori, Andrea and Maggie deal with a suicidal Beth.', 2, 10, '26 Feb. 2012'),
(597, 'tt1804263', '12', 'Judge, Jury, Executioner', 'MV5BMTk0OTE2NzExOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTc2MDg0Nw@@', 'Dale fears the group is losing its humanity as Rick and the others vote to execute Randall.', 2, 11, '4 Mar. 2012'),
(598, 'tt1804264', '12', 'Better Angels', 'MV5BMjIxMjM0Njc2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDQ5MjE1Nw@@', 'Shane''s antagonistic behaviour reaches new heights, while Carl suffers the consequences of his actions.', 2, 12, '11 Mar. 2012'),
(599, 'tt1804265', '12', 'Beside the Dying Fire', 'MV5BMTQyODk0MjczN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTQyMDg1Nw@@', 'As the farm is overrun by walkers, the group fights to escape.', 2, 13, '18 Mar. 2012'),
(600, 'tt2107527', '12', 'Seed', 'MV5BMTAxMTYzODgyNzFeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDU0ODc2OTc@', 'After months on the run, the group take refuge in a federal prison, while elsewhere, Andrea''s health starts to deteriorate.', 3, 1, '14 Oct. 2012'),
(601, 'tt2253598', '12', 'Sick', 'MV5BMjEwNTMxNzYyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzcyMDM1OA@@', 'As Hershel''s condition worsens, Rick, Daryl and T-Dog deal with a group of prisoners.', 3, 2, '21 Oct. 2012'),
(602, 'tt2253600', '12', 'Walk with Me', 'MV5BMTQ3NzQzNTI2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzAyMDM1OA@@', 'Andrea and Michonne are brought to a walled community run by a man called The Governor.', 3, 3, '28 Oct. 2012'),
(603, 'tt2253602', '12', 'Killer Within', 'MV5BMTY0NDg2NjU3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTcyMDM1OA@@', 'Lori goes into labour when the prison comes under attack. Michonne tries to convince Andrea to leave Woodbury.', 3, 4, '4 Nov. 2012'),
(604, 'tt2253610', '12', 'Say the Word', 'MV5BOTEzNjM3MTE1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDQzMDM1OA@@', 'Rick struggles to cope. Andrea and Michonne part ways. Daryl and Maggie head out to find food and clothes for the baby.', 3, 5, '11 Nov. 2012'),
(605, 'tt2253604', '12', 'Hounded', 'MV5BNzM1NjA5Mzc5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjk0MjQ3OA@@', 'Rick receives a mysterious phone call. Andrea grows closer to The Governor. Merle tries to hunt down Michonne.', 3, 6, '18 Nov. 2012'),
(606, 'tt2253606', '12', 'When the Dead Come Knocking', 'MV5BMTgyNzIzNjEzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjQxOTc3OA@@', 'Michonne leads Rick, Daryl and Oscar to Woodbury to rescue Glenn and Maggie. Merle tries to force information out of Glenn.', 3, 7, '25 Nov. 2012'),
(607, 'tt2253608', '12', 'Made to Suffer', 'MV5BMTg0MTI2MTgxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTQxOTc3OA@@', 'Rick, Daryl, Michonne and Oscar enter Woodbury in search of Glenn and Maggie. Meanwhile, a new group of survivors encounter the prison.', 3, 8, '2 Dec. 2012'),
(608, 'tt2269550', '12', 'The Suicide King', 'MV5BMTQ1MjEyMjkxMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzMwNzMwOQ@@', 'Woodbury is left in disarray following the attack by Rick''s group. Merle''s presence in the group causes conflict.', 3, 9, '10 Feb. 2013'),
(609, 'tt2401094', '12', 'Home', 'MV5BMTgxODQ3NTU4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjk5NTAxOQ@@', 'Rick continues to see visions of Lori. The Governor plans an assault on the prison. Daryl and Merle fend for themselves out in the forest.', 3, 10, '17 Feb. 2013'),
(610, 'tt2521154', '12', 'I Ain''t a Judas', 'MV5BMTgwNTQxMzk5Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjY4NDMxOQ@@', 'As Rick and the group debate their next course of action, Andrea tries to negotiate with them. Meanwhile, The Governor prepares Woodbury for battle.', 3, 11, '24 Feb. 2013'),
(611, 'tt2521158', '12', 'Clear', 'MV5BMjMzNzg5OTU2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTcwMDIyOQ@@', 'Rick runs into a familiar face when he, Carl and Michonne head back to Rick''s hometown for more guns to fortify themselves against The Governor.', 3, 12, '3 Mar. 2013'),
(612, 'tt2521162', '12', 'Arrow on the Doorpost', 'MV5BNjA0OTcyOTI2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTYwMDIyOQ@@', 'Rick and The Governor meet face-to-face, ostensibly to make a peaceful resolution to prevent further bloodshed. Back at the prison, tensions arise between Merle and the rest of the group.', 3, 13, '10 Mar. 2013'),
(613, 'tt2521168', '12', 'Prey', 'MV5BMjE4MzY1NDU5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzczNDUyOQ@@', 'The Governor hunts down Andrea when she flees Woodbury. Meanwhile, tensions arise within Tyreese''s group, and The Governor''s plan for Rick''s group is sabotaged.', 3, 14, '17 Mar. 2013'),
(614, 'tt2521172', '12', 'This Sorrowful Life', 'MV5BMTkzMzU1ODI1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTgyNTYyOQ@@', 'While Rick decides the fate of Michonne, Merle takes matters into his own hand.', 3, 15, '24 Mar. 2013'),
(615, 'tt2521182', '12', 'Welcome to the Tombs', 'MV5BMjA2MDIxNTgyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTY2ODAzOQ@@', 'As Rick and the group prepare for the Governor''s impending attack, Andrea fights to escape captivity.', 3, 16, '31 Mar. 2013'),
(616, 'tt2795750', '12', '30 Days Without an Accident', 'MV5BNjI2MDYzOTkwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzI3MDMzMDE@', 'Several months have passed and Rick and the expanded group are living a more peaceful life at the prison. Problems surface when Rick encounters a new survivor, and a supply run ends in disaster.', 4, 1, '13 Oct. 2013'),
(617, 'tt2931446', '12', 'Infected', 'MV5BMTg4NzYyMjA1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDg2MDMzMDE@', 'Rick is forced to abandon his quiet lifestyle when a mysterious virus puts the lives of everyone at the prison at risk.', 4, 2, '20 Oct. 2013'),
(618, 'tt2948632', '12', 'Isolation', 'MV5BMTk2MjkxNDMyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzM3MDMzMDE@', 'As the sick are quarantined, Daryl, Tyreese, Michonne and Bob leave the prison in search of medical supplies. Rick makes a shocking discovery.', 4, 3, '27 Oct. 2013'),
(619, 'tt2948628', '12', 'Indifference', 'MV5BMjAyMzI2NDIzM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzU0MzE1MDE@', 'Daryl, Tyreese, Michonne and Bob continue to the veterinary college on foot in search of medicine. Rick and Carol go on a run to a nearby town where they find two uninfected stragglers.', 4, 4, '3 Nov. 2013'),
(620, 'tt2948636', '12', 'Internment', 'MV5BMjY2MTk5MjcwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk2MDMzMDE@', 'Hershel struggles to care for the sick as the situation in the cell block escalates. Meanwhile, Rick and Carl defend the prison as the fences give way.', 4, 5, '10 Nov. 2013'),
(621, 'tt2948630', '12', 'Live Bait', 'MV5BMTQzODcwODY4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzAwMDU2MDE@', 'The Governor bonds with a small family following the downfall of Woodbury.', 4, 6, '17 Nov. 2013'),
(622, 'tt2948634', '12', 'Dead Weight', 'MV5BMjI2MDA0NTMwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA2ODY2MDE@', 'The Governor plans his next move as he, Lilly, Tara and Meghan adjust to new surroundings.', 4, 7, '24 Nov. 2013'),
(623, 'tt2948638', '12', 'Too Far Gone', 'MV5BMjMxNDA5ODcyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDUzNzI3MDE@', 'Rick and the group face imminent danger as The Governor and his army arrive to take the prison.', 4, 8, '1 Dec. 2013'),
(624, 'tt3316798', '12', 'After', 'MV5BMjM2MTAyNzk5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjM2ODQxMTE@', 'With the prison overrun, Rick and Carl find themselves on the road looking for shelter. Meanwhile, Michonne is haunted by memories of the past.', 4, 9, '9 Feb. 2014'),
(625, 'tt3260594', '12', 'Inmates', 'MV5BMjE4ODUxMDg3NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI1NjkxMTE@', 'Beth tries to remain hopeful. Tyreese, Lizzie and Mika run into a familiar face. Glenn and Maggie struggle to cope without each other.', 4, 10, '16 Feb. 2014'),
(626, 'tt3316794', '12', 'Claimed', 'MV5BMjkyOTcyODk1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM1NjQyMTE@', 'While Carl and Michonne look for supplies, Rick is faced against a gang of marauders. Meanwhile, Glenn and Tara are brought together with three strangers on an important mission.', 4, 11, '23 Feb. 2014'),
(627, 'tt3259044', '12', 'Still', 'MV5BMTY4ODU3OTE5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA5NzgyMTE@', 'Daryl and Beth seek refuge in the woods, where conflict emerges between the pair.', 4, 12, '2 Mar. 2014'),
(628, 'tt3316796', '12', 'Alone', 'MV5BMTY4NTU2NDI2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY5MjQzMTE@', 'Maggie, Sasha and Bob clash over whether they should head to Terminus. Daryl and Beth take shelter in a seemingly abandoned funeral home.', 4, 13, '9 Mar. 2014'),
(629, 'tt3316800', '12', 'The Grove', 'MV5BMTgzMzg1NjYzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQyODM0MTE@', 'Carol has to cope with old secrets and Lizzie''s psychotic behavior when she, Tyreese and the girls take refuge in a vacant house on the way to Terminus.', 4, 14, '16 Mar. 2014'),
(630, 'tt3260610', '12', 'Us', 'MV5BNTYwNDg5NDk4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDAyODM0MTE@', 'Glenn and Tara are set on the way to Terminus, but Abraham is reluctant. Daryl struggles to adjust to the Claimers'' rules.', 4, 15, '23 Mar. 2014'),
(631, 'tt3260612', '12', 'A', 'MV5BMTgzNDU2Nzk3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTQ0NDg0MTE@', 'Rick, Carl and Michonne cross paths with the Claimers once again on the way to Terminus, as the so-called sanctuary begins to reveal its true face.', 4, 16, '30 Mar. 2014'),
(632, 'tt3297776', '12', 'No Sanctuary', 'MV5BMTgwOTcyMjg5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI4ODEwMzE@', 'Carol takes drastic action to rescue Rick and the group from the cannibals of Terminus as she and Tyreese reach the compound.', 5, 1, '12 Oct. 2014'),
(633, 'tt3646000', '12', 'Strangers', 'MV5BMzY1OTk3NzQ0Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODk2ODEwMzE@', 'Out of Terminus, the group cross paths with a mysterious priest and take shelter in his church. As Daryl and Carol follow a lead to the whereabouts of Beth, the others begin to realize that they''re being hunted.', 5, 2, '19 Oct. 2014'),
(634, 'tt3689244', '12', 'Four Walls and a Roof', 'MV5BMjAzNzA5NTgxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzkyODMwMzE@', 'As Bob''s life hangs in the balance, the group prepare to face off against Gareth and the hunters of Terminus.', 5, 3, '26 Oct. 2014'),
(635, 'tt3712494', '12', 'Slabtown', 'MV5BMjI4NDc5NjM2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk0ODgzMzE@', 'After being separated from Daryl, Beth finds herself in Grady Memorial Hospital in Atlanta, now controlled by what''s left of the police force.', 5, 4, '2 Nov. 2014'),
(636, 'tt3714480', '12', 'Self Help', 'MV5BNDIyNDI1NTg3MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE1ODgzMzE@', 'As Glenn, Maggie, Abraham and co. head to D.C., a new revelation threatens to put the whole journey to a halt.', 5, 5, '9 Nov. 2014'),
(637, 'tt3714484', '12', 'Consumed', 'MV5BMzE5NDU3MTAwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjEyNzQ0MzE@', 'Daryl and Carol chase the white-crossed car to a desolated Atlanta with hopes of finding Beth and her kidnappers.', 5, 6, '16 Nov. 2014'),
(638, 'tt3714490', '12', 'Crossed', 'MV5BMTUwOTUyODkzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc5NDc0MzE@', 'While Carl, Michonne and Gabriel hold down the church, Rick takes a rescue mission to Atlanta, as Abraham''s group deal with the fallout from Eugene''s revelation.', 5, 7, '23 Nov. 2014'),
