(934, 'tt1995102', '17', 'Meet the New Boss', 'MV5BMTg4NDYxOTgzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODIxMjYyMjE@', 'Castiel believes he is the new God and becomes obsessed with power. Sam, Dean, and Bobby try to find a way to stop him before he explodes with power, even if that means talking to Death himself.', 7, 1, '23 Sep. 2011'),
