(1311, 'tt4061178', '21', 'Dr. Linus Creel (No. 82)', 'MV5BMzg5NzcxNzE2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzkxODk4MjE@', 'After a series of seemingly nonviolent citizens become killers, Red tips off Liz that a dangerous social-psychological experiment may be underway. Elsewhere, Red tries to convince Naomi and her husband into accepting a complicated proposition.', 2, 4, '13 Oct. 2014'),
