(2204, 'tt1054726', '32', 'Cancer Man', 'MV5BODg5MTYzNzM4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDAwOTc5MjE@', 'Walt tells the rest of his family about his cancer. Jesse tries to make amends with his own parents.', 1, 4, '17 Feb. 2008'),
(2205, 'tt1054727', '32', 'Gray Matter', 'MV5BNTkxMjg1MTU5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODAwOTc5MjE@', 'Walt rejects everyone who tries to help him with the cancer. Jesse tries his best to create Walt''s meth, with the help of an old friend.', 1, 5, '24 Feb. 2008'),
(2206, 'tt1054728', '32', 'Crazy Handful of Nothin''', 'MV5BMTY0MzYxOTEwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjAwOTc5MjE@', 'With the side effects and cost of his treatment mounting, Walt demands that Jesse finds a wholesaler to buy their drugs, which lands him in trouble.', 1, 6, '2 Mar. 2008'),
(2207, 'tt1054729', '32', 'A No-Rough-Stuff-Type Deal', 'MV5BMTkwOTQ1MjA2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTAwOTc5MjE@', 'Walt and Jesse try to up their game by making more of the crystal every week for Tuco. Unfortunately, some of the ingredients they need are not easy to find. Meanwhile, Skyler realizes that her sister is a shoplifter.', 1, 7, '9 Mar. 2008'),
(2208, 'tt1232244', '32', 'Seven Thirty-Seven', 'MV5BNzE4NDM2NjY5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDcwNDc1NjE@', 'After witnessing Tuco murder one of his junkies, Walt and Jesse fear that he will kill them next, to tie up loose ends. Unless they kill Tuco first.', 2, 1, '8 Mar. 2009'),
(2209, 'tt1232249', '32', 'Grilled', 'MV5BMTkwODEyMTcxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzM5NjA0Mg@@', 'Tuco takes Walt and Jesse prisoner.', 2, 2, '15 Mar. 2009'),
(2210, 'tt1232250', '32', 'Bit by a Dead Bee', 'MV5BMTc1NDYxMDM3OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE4OTc5MjE@', 'Walt and Jesse try to come up with alibis for their disappearances.', 2, 3, '22 Mar. 2009'),
(2211, 'tt1232251', '32', 'Down', 'MV5BMjI0NzA3MDc0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTE4OTc5MjE@', 'Skyler keeps mysteriously leaving without talking to Walt. Jesse''s parents throw him out of his own house.', 2, 4, '29 Mar. 2009'),
(2212, 'tt1232252', '32', 'Breakage', 'MV5BMTkyMjI5NjQ5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE4OTc5MjE@', 'Walt and Jesse decide to start their own little empire with the help of Jesse''s friends: Skinny Pete, Combo, and Badger. Meanwhile, Hank tries to pull himself together after his encounter with Tuco.', 2, 5, '5 Apr. 2009'),
(2213, 'tt1232253', '32', 'Peekaboo', 'MV5BMTc3NzQ0NjQ1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjE4OTc5MjE@', 'After Skinny Pete gets ripped off, Walt makes Jesse go get the money. Meanwhile, Walt''s cover story on how Elliott and Gretchen are paying for his medical treatment is on the verge of collapsing.', 2, 6, '12 Apr. 2009'),
(2214, 'tt1232254', '32', 'Negro Y Azul', 'MV5BMTQ0MDU0Nzc3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI4OTc5MjE@', 'Rumor is spreading that Jesse killed the man that ripped Skinny Pete off. Walt uses this to his advantage on expanding their territory. Meanwhile, Hank has been promoted to the El Paso office. But it''s not all he hoped it would be.', 2, 7, '19 Apr. 2009'),
(2215, 'tt1232255', '32', 'Better Call Saul', 'MV5BMTQyNDIxMDcwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjI4OTc5MjE@', 'Badger is caught by the DEA. Walt and Jesse hire the best criminal lawyer in town, Saul Goodman.', 2, 8, '26 Apr. 2009'),
(2216, 'tt1232256', '32', '4 Days Out', 'MV5BMTg5MjIzODI4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI4OTc5MjE@', 'Walt and Jesse become stranded out in the middle of the desert after cooking more crystal.', 2, 9, '3 May 2009'),
(2217, 'tt1232245', '32', 'Over', 'MV5BMTcyMTA2NzgxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI4OTc5MjE@', 'Walt''s cancer has greatly improved. Time to celebrate. Meanwhile Jesse tries to meet his new girlfriend''s father.', 2, 10, '10 May 2009'),
(2218, 'tt1232246', '32', 'Mandala', 'MV5BMjAxNjE0MTYzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI4OTc5MjE@', 'Combo is found dead. Walt and Jesse''s little empire begins to crumble. Saul tries to set them up with a mysterious distributor.', 2, 11, '17 May 2009'),
(2219, 'tt1232247', '32', 'Phoenix', 'MV5BMjA1OTI0NzUwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzM4OTc5MjE@', 'Walt and Skyler have a baby girl. Now that Jesse is hooked on heroin, Walt refuses to give him his money until he gets clean. Meanwhile, as an excuse for his money, Walt decides to donate the money to himself through his son''s new website.', 2, 12, '24 May 2009'),
(2220, 'tt1232248', '32', 'ABQ', 'MV5BMTY2NjY3NzM0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzE4OTc5MjE@', 'Walt''s lies have pushed Skyler to her limit. She leaves with the kids. Meanwhile, Jesse blames himself for Jane''s death and goes into rehab.', 2, 13, '31 May 2009'),
(2221, 'tt1528116', '32', 'No Más', 'MV5BMTU0NTY0MDU2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDUzMDg5MjE@', 'Skyler is planning to divorce Walt now that she knows about the crystal meth. Jesse finishes rehab.', 3, 1, '21 Mar. 2010'),
(2222, 'tt1615186', '32', 'Caballo sin Nombre', 'MV5BMjAxMzg0NDE3OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDYxMDg5MjE@', 'Walter Jr is having a rough time accepting his parents'' separation. Jesse buys his old house from his parents. Meanwhile, two mysterious men have come into town looking for Walt.', 3, 2, '28 Mar. 2010'),
(2223, 'tt1615187', '32', 'I.F.T.', 'MV5BMTMyMTgzNDA3MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTMwMTIzMw@@', 'Walt has moved back into the house without Skyler''s consent. Now she can''t get him out. Meanwhile, Jesse continues to cope with Jane''s death.', 3, 3, '4 Apr. 2010'),
(2224, 'tt1615554', '32', 'Green Light', 'MV5BMTc5NzE3NTc0MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDk5MDIzMw@@', 'Walt''s world crumbles even more when he finds out that Skyler is cheating on him. Jesse tries to set up a meeting with Gus to try and sell his own version of the blue meth. Meanwhile, Hank is growing obsessed with finding Heisenberg.', 3, 4, '11 Apr. 2010'),
(2225, 'tt1615555', '32', 'Más', 'MV5BMjA1NzQ1ODM0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjg0MDYzMw@@', 'Gus tries to get Walt back in the business by offering him three million dollars and a brand new lab. Jesse is furious that Walt received half of the money for his blue meth. Hank tries to track down the RV meth lab.', 3, 5, '18 Apr. 2010'),
(2226, 'tt1615556', '32', 'Sunset', 'MV5BMjEzNjI4MDI0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTkxMTgzMw@@', 'Walt''s new business and assistant, Gale, are making his life much easier. Hank trails the RV back to Jesse. When Walt finds out, he tries to destroy the RV.', 3, 6, '25 Apr. 2010'),
(2227, 'tt1615944', '32', 'One Minute', 'MV5BMTQ1MjUxNDIwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDcxMDg5MjE@', 'Jesse ends up in the hospital after getting beaten up by Hank. Now he is threatening to press charges against the DEA. To stop him, Walt decides to bring Jesse on as his partner, once again.', 3, 7, '2 May 2010'),
(2228, 'tt1615557', '32', 'I See You', 'MV5BMjI2NDU5OTI0MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzYxMDg5MjE@', 'Hank ends up in the hospital after being attacked by Tuco''s cousins. Walt spends too much time by his family''s side when he should be cooking meth.', 3, 8, '9 May 2010');
