(2426, 'tt3460686', '36', 'Basketsball', 'MV5BMjI5MTA3Mzk1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTkwOTEyMjE@', 'Jess pretends to be a fan of the Pistons in an attempt to befriend Coach, to Nick''s dismay, who is a Bulls fan. Meanwhile, Schmidt is assigned to mentor an elderly colleague at work and Winston discovers a new career path.', 3, 12, '14 Jan. 2014'),
(2427, 'tt3352334', '36', 'Birthday', 'MV5BMTUwOTU1ODYyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTAxNDc5MjE@', 'Nick struggles to throw Jess the perfect birthday party. Schmidt works overtime to help out Cece in her new job as bartender. Winston and Coach engage in a bake-off.', 3, 13, '21 Jan. 2014'),
