(2441, 'tt4064296', '36', 'Micro', 'MV5BMTc4MDE4NDI0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTM2OTU4MjE@', 'Nick hatches a bet with Jess that she''s just as superficial as the rest of the guys when it comes to dating. Meanwhile, Winston and Cece team up to trick Schmidt and Coach into thinking they''re going to be models.', 4, 4, '7 Oct. 2014'),
(2442, 'tt4085018', '36', 'Landline', 'MV5BMjE4NzM4MDY5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjA3NTIwMzE@', 'When Coach''s liaison with the school nurse gets messy, vice principal Jess must enforce a new, "no fraternization" policy among the teachers. But the tables soon get turned when she finds herself attracted to the hot new science teacher. Meanwhile, Nick i', 4, 5, '14 Oct. 2014'),
(2443, 'tt4085022', '36', 'Background Check', 'MV5BMTc5NTIwNzIyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI3NjkzMzE@', 'Jess admits she might be in possession of certain illegal substances, which complicates Winston''s plans as the loft must pass a home visit and a background check as a part of his police academy training.', 4, 6, '4 Nov. 2014'),
(2444, 'tt4085026', '36', 'Goldmine', 'MV5BMTc4NDAwMDMyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDUwOTgzMzE@', 'Nick pretends to be gay so that Jess''s new boyfriend will feel less threatened. Coach is annoyed at Winston for working his "Long Game" on two attractive neighbors. Meanwhile, Schmidt is bummed to learn Cece is considering having her breasts reduced.', 4, 7, '11 Nov. 2014'),
(2445, 'tt4085024', '36', 'Teachers', 'MV5BODczNzc3NjM2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQwOTgzMzE@', 'Jess, Coach and Ryan attend a teacher''s conference, led by education guru Brenda Brown. Back at the loft, Nick, Schmidt and Winston try to have a wild weekend while Jess is out of town.', 4, 8, '18 Nov. 2014'),
(2446, 'tt4085028', '36', 'Thanksgiving IV', 'MV5BMTA3NzQ4MjQ4MDNeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDg5OTQ5NDMx', 'With winter coming and everyone still single, Schmidt initiates a "Bangs-giving"-themed Thanksgiving dinner party, to which everyone must bring someone compatible for someone else.', 4, 9, '25 Nov. 2014'),
(2447, 'tt4085030', '36', 'Girl Fight', 'MV5BMTk2MTQxODQxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTY5OTI2MzE@', 'Schmidt quickly regrets trying to understand the politics of a girl fight when one breaks out between Jess and Cece. Meanwhile, Nick goes on a date with Tran''s granddaughter, whom Winston believes is hiding a secret.', 4, 10, '2 Dec. 2014'),
(2448, 'tt4232492', '36', 'LAXmas', 'MV5BMjM3Nzk1NDE0Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDYxNTU2MzE@', 'As the gang prepares to depart for the holidays, they quickly find they may be home alone when they are all trapped at the airport.', 4, 11, '9 Dec. 2014'),
(2449, 'tt4333024', '36', 'Shark', 'MV5BMjMxMjY3NjYyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTM1MTk3NDE@', 'Nick and Coach become concerned when they meet Winston''s new training officer; Jess uses Schmidt in hope of influencing a councilwoman to stop the night construction taking place outside the loft.', 4, 12, '6 Jan. 2015'),
