(2571, 'tt3461006', '38', 'Insatiable', 'MV5BMjA0NzQ3MTM4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDc3ODEzMjE@', 'Scott and company race to rescue Lydia from the clutches of evil as the Nogitsune makes a surprise move, resulting in a tragic loss to the group.', 3, 24, '17 Mar. 2014'),
(2572, 'tt3461002', '38', 'The Divine Move', 'MV5BNzQxMTA1NzgyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY3ODEzMjE@', 'Struck by disaster and nearly defeated, Scott and Derek call on their friends and allies to make one last stand.', 3, 25, '24 Mar. 2014'),
(2573, 'tt3256392', '38', 'The Dark Moon', 'MV5BMjA3NjU4NDE2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjk3Mzc5MjE@', 'After the heartache of losing two of their own, Scott has an unexpected visit from an old friend. Does this mean they can reunite their pack or are there evil intentions at play?', 4, 1, '23 Jun. 2014'),
