(2576, 'tt3841382', '38', 'The Benefactor', 'MV5BMTkyNjM0OTAyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzgyMTg5MjE@', 'The team has their hands full with Liam and Malia when the full moon arrives. The ''Axe Murderer'' harms Peter and reveals that Derek is next on his ''list''. Lydia cracks the code and finds a list of all supernatural creatures in the town.', 4, 4, '14 Jul. 2014'),
(2577, 'tt3841386', '38', 'I.E.D.', 'MV5BMjMwNjkwODUxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjgxMzIzMjE@', 'As another name is scratched off the list, Lydia is required to find the second key, thus revealing more targets. Scott, Stiles and Kira are on high alert after realizing that the assassin is on the lacrosse team.', 4, 5, '21 Jul. 2014'),
(2578, 'tt3842518', '38', 'Orphaned', 'MV5BMjI4NDA3OTAyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQyMTg5MjE@', 'With Violet''s arrest, Garrett forces Scott to help get her back by using Liam as a bargaining chip. Stiles, Lydia and Jordan seek Meredith''s help to uncover the third key.', 4, 6, '28 Jul. 2014'),
(2579, 'tt3843946', '38', 'Weaponized', 'MV5BMTgyMzkxNjM4MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODcwMjg5MjE@', 'A frantic call to the CDC has everyone paranoid, especially since it was designed to target werewolves. Scott, Malia and Kira lock themselves in the Hale vault, unaware of their salvation within their grasp.', 4, 7, '4 Aug. 2014'),
(2580, 'tt3842522', '38', 'Time of Death', 'MV5BMTc1NzEyNzQ5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTUyMTg5MjE@', 'With Noshiko''s help, the team come up with a plan hoping to reveal the benefactor''s identity. But Kate''s arrival threatens to ruin it all. Malia comes face-to-face with Peter in the Hale vault, thus delving into her past.', 4, 8, '11 Aug. 2014'),
(2581, 'tt3842524', '38', 'Perishable', 'MV5BMTU0Mjg0MzQzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODM2Mjg5MjE@', 'After a vain attempt to kill Parrish, it''s clear that almost everyone has access to the dead-pool. Lydia dives into her grandmother''s past, uncovering yet another list which leads her to Eichen House. The team soon realizes no one is safe.', 4, 9, '18 Aug. 2014'),
(2582, 'tt3842530', '38', 'Monstrous', 'MV5BMjM0Njk4OTk1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTYyMTg5MjE@', 'Meredith is brought in for questioning, but refuses to talk to anyone but Peter. Stiles and Malia head over to the lake house wherein lies the dead-pool. Scott, Derek, Kira and some others take a stand against the assassins out for blood.', 4, 10, '24 Aug. 2014'),
