(2615, 'tt1973786', '39', 'Pilot', 'MV5BMTU2NjA5MzI5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDU3MjYyMjE@', 'A "closer" for one of New York City''s most successful law firms decides to hire an aloof genius who has passed the bar but never went to law school as his associate.', 1, 1, '23 Jun. 2011'),
