(2619, 'tt2003931', '39', 'Bail Out', 'MV5BMTU4NzM4MTE1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDY0MDYyMjE@', 'Harvey is a witness for his driver in a civil suit, and has to rely on Louis for help. Mike bails his old friend Trevor out of jail.', 1, 5, '21 Jul. 2011'),
(2620, 'tt1973787', '39', 'Tricks of the Trade', 'MV5BMTk3MDg3NzY3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTU3MjYyMjE@', 'Harvey and Mike try to prove that a woman accused of insider trading is innocent. Mike also tries to help Rachel study for the LSAT, but he soon finds out she is close to uncovering his secret.', 1, 6, '28 Jul. 2011'),
(2621, 'tt1987364', '39', 'Play the Man', 'MV5BOTA0NDYwMTAxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzEwMTYyMjE@', 'Mike takes on Louis'' protégé during a mock trial, but his conflict with Rachel could hurt his chances of winning. Elsewhere, Harvey works on a merger between two hotel chains, but his past with the opposing counsel complicates matters.', 1, 7, '4 Aug. 2011'),
(2622, 'tt1987365', '39', 'Identity Crisis', 'MV5BMTY3MDcwNzY3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQwMTYyMjE@', 'Harvey and Louis come to blows after Louis'' reckless behavior threatens to cost the firm a case, while Mike is assigned to a businessman who is trying to get back money from his estranged daughter.', 1, 8, '11 Aug. 2011'),
(2623, 'tt1985804', '39', 'Undefeated', 'MV5BMjM3NDA3MzY0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTYzNDUyMjE@', 'Harvey meets his match in a cocky opposing counsel in a class action lawsuit, and Mike unknowingly helps frame Rachel as a traitor to the firm.', 1, 9, '18 Aug. 2011'),
(2624, 'tt1986650', '39', 'The Shelf Life', 'MV5BNTg2MjQyMDg2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjg3NDUyMjE@', 'Harvey must fire an accountant for falsifying his credentials, but Mike finds a more sinister motive for his termination and becomes concerned about his own employment. Meanwhile, Louis thinks he''s found his future wife.', 1, 10, '25 Aug. 2011'),
