(2637, 'tt2583678', '39', 'Blind-Sided', 'MV5BMTY0NjY5NTc4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjgwMTc5OA@@', 'Mike gets too emotional when Harvey asks him to negotiate a hit-and-run settlement, and Louis runs into trouble as he tries to hire his first associate.', 2, 11, '17 Jan. 2013'),
