(2924, 'tt4064654', '42', 'Smash the Mirror: Part 1', 'MV5BMTc2Mjg0MjM0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA0MjM0MzE@', 'Gold interferes with the Snow Queen''s plans for his own agenda, as flashbacks show the Snow Queen try to pit Elsa and Anna against each other. Emma turns to Gold for help getting her powers under control.', 4, 9, '16 Nov. 2014'),
(2925, 'tt4589038', '42', 'Smash the Mirror: Part 2', '01', 'As everyone races to stop Emma from giving up her powers, Robin finds a clue that could point Regina to the elusive author of the storybook.', 4, 10, '16 Nov. 2014'),
(2926, 'tt4105490', '42', 'Fall', 'MV5BNTUyNTEyOTEwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDM3Mjg1MzE@', 'As the Spell of Shattered Sight approaches Storybrooke, Emma and Elsa search for Anna, Belle and the fairies work on an antidote, and Gold, with a reluctant Hook as his servant, works on an exit strategy.', 4, 11, '30 Nov. 2014'),
(2927, 'tt4129344', '42', 'Shattered Sight', 'MV5BMjE3MDg5MjkwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg3Mjg1MzE@', 'As the Spell of Shattered Sight hits Storybrooke, Emma and Elsa race against the clock to free themselves of the ribbons and take down the Snow Queen.', 4, 12, '7 Dec. 2014'),
(2928, 'tt4142072', '42', 'Heroes and Villains', 'MV5BMjMwOTI4ODYwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzYwNzI3MzE@', 'In the aftermath of the Snow Queen''s curse; Emma looks for a portal so Elsa, Anna and Kristoff can return to Arendelle, Regina makes a difficult choice, and Gold''s quest for power reaches a dramatic conclusion.', 4, 13, '14 Dec. 2014'),
(2929, 'tt4203690', '42', 'Darkness on the Edge of Town', 'MV5BMTA2Mzk4OTQ4NjJeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDQ3NDEyNDQx', 'Hook and Belle search for a way to release the fairies from the Sorcerer''s hat, Emma, Regina and Henry continue to look for clues that could lead them to the Author, and Gold and Ursula enlist Cruella to join their cause, as flashbacks show their first me', 4, 14, '1 Mar. 2015'),
(2930, 'tt4230126', '42', 'Unforgiven', 'MV5BMjExMjcyMzY4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTQ1NzA3NDE@', 'Regina and Henry turn to Marco and Pinocchio for help in their quest to find the Author. Emma worries that Mary Margaret and David are hiding something from her as they remain wary of Cruella and Ursula.', 4, 15, '8 Mar. 2015'),
(2931, 'tt4273302', '42', 'Enter the Dragon', 'MV5BMjI4NjYxMzM5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTgxODc4NDE@', 'In order to infiltrate the Queens of Darkness as a spy, Regina has to prove that she is still a villain. Meanwhile, Hook asks Belle for an unusual favor, and Henry makes progress on his search for the Author.', 4, 16, '15 Mar. 2015'),
(2932, 'tt4282636', '42', 'Poor Unfortunate Soul', 'MV5BMTA2NTEwNTk1MjBeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDUxOTc4OTQx', 'Hook tries to make a deal with Ursula as flashbacks show their complicated past, while Regina struggles to maintain her cover with Gold, Cruella and Maleficent.', 4, 17, '22 Mar. 2015'),
(2933, 'tt4282632', '42', 'Best Laid Plans', 'MV5BMjIyMzczOTQ5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjkyMTExNTE@', 'Maleficent puts Storybrooke under a sleeping curse in an attempt to steal the page that the Author is trapped inside. Mary Margaret and David struggle with their guilt as flashbacks show them go to extreme lengths to protect their unborn child from darkne', 4, 18, '29 Mar. 2015'),
(2934, 'tt4282640', '42', 'Heart of Gold', 'MV5BMjI0OTU0NDE2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODMwMzYyNTE@', 'The Author joins forces with Gold and Regina fears for Robin''s safety, as flashbacks show what happened to Robin after leaving Storybrooke with Marian and Roland.', 4, 19, '12 Apr. 2015');
