(2935, 'tt4282638', '42', 'Sympathy for the De Vil', 'MV5BMTY4MzUzMzgxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzAzMTczNTE@', 'Regina''s plans to head to New York to rescue Robin from Zelena are halted when Cruella kidnaps Henry, as flashbacks show her encounter the Author, who encourages her to stand up to her oppressive mother.', 4, 20, '19 Apr. 2015'),
(2936, 'tt4282642', '42', 'Lily', 'MV5BMTk4NzE1OTE1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTg1NDY0NTE@', 'Emma realizes Maleficent''s daughter is her former childhood friend Lily and leaves Storybrooke with Regina to find her, as well as to rescue Robin from Zelena.', 4, 21, '26 Apr. 2015'),
(2937, 'tt4282648', '42', 'Mother', 'MV5BOTkyMDQzMzc3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQyMDU1NTE@', 'Emma reunites Maleficent with Lily, who is still hell bent on seeking revenge against Mary Margaret and David. Meanwhile, Regina and Robin struggle to cope with the implications of Zelena''s pregnancy.', 4, 22, '3 May 2015'),
(2938, 'tt4282650', '42', 'Operation Mongoose: Part 1', 'MV5BMTA1NTUwMjM4MzheQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDk0OTY2NjUx', 'The Author proves to be a formidable wild card and forges an alliance with Gold. Emma, her parents, Hook and Regina scramble to stop them, but when Gold and the Author turn the tables on heroes and villains alike, the prospect of any happy outcome appears', 4, 23, '10 May 2015'),
(2939, 'tt4500028', '42', 'Operation Mongoose: Part 2', 'MV5BMTU2ODIyMTc5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ5NjY2NTE@', 'The author aligns with Gold, while Emma, her parents, Hook and Regina try to stop them; Henry steps up to save his family.', 4, 24, '10 May 2015'),
(2940, 'tt4673478', '42', 'The Dark Swan', 'MV5BMTQ0NTY1ODA5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTMyMTI4NjE@', 'With Emma now facing the nature of the Darkness in herself, she encounters Merida. Her family and friends go to extreme measurements to find Emma and bring her home safely.', 5, 1, '27 Sep. 2015'),
(2941, 'tt4799910', '42', 'The Price', 'MV5BMjA0Mzc5MzcwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTIwNDYyNzE@', 'While Prince Arthur organizes a ball in Camelot, darkness rises in Storybrooke, to the search of a savior.', 5, 2, '4 Oct. 2015'),
(2942, 'tt4799912', '42', 'Siege Perilous', 'MV5BNzI4NDY2OTEyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTYwNDYyNzE@', 'A royal ball is held in Camelot, but a dark turn of events forces David and Robin to take action. Meanwhile, Regina''s fortitude is tested as she tries to safeguard Emma; and back in Storybrooke, Hook attempts to bring Emma back to the light.', 5, 3, '11 Oct. 2015'),
(2943, 'tt4799914', '42', 'The Broken Kingdom', 'MV5BMTU3Njk1MzM2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTIxNDYyNzE@', 'In Rumplestiltskin return, Emma takes her chance at the taking of Excalibur, while King Arthur''s real identity is revealed.', 5, 4, '18 Oct. 2015'),
(2944, 'tt4799922', '42', 'Dreamcatcher', 'MV5BMjM4ODEyMTU5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTEyNDYyNzE@', 'Emma and Regina devise a plan to free Merlin, but they lack a pivotal ingredient. Meanwhile, Mary Margaret and David seek an important dagger; Henry asks Violet to go on a date; and Merida attempts to carry out a covert mission Emma has assigned her.', 5, 5, '25 Oct. 2015'),
(2945, 'tt4868836', '42', 'The Bear and the Bow', 'MV5BMTU0ODI4OTgxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTYyNDYyNzE@', 'Gold and Merida are tested to their limits, can they be the heroes they need to be? King Arthur''s help is needed to contact Merlin but can he be trusted', 5, 6, '1 Nov. 2015'),
(2946, 'tt4799960', '42', 'Nimue', 'MV5BNzQ5MzM2NTQ0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTAzNDYyNzE@', 'Emma''s darkness is tested while she has an encounter with the first "dark one". The history of Excalibur is revealed.', 5, 7, '8 Nov. 2015'),
(2947, 'tt4799998', '42', 'Birth', 'MV5BMTg4MTU1OTg0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjczNDYyNzE@', 'Hook risks everything to uncover the truth about what Emma did in Camelot.', 5, 8, '15 Nov. 2015'),
(2948, 'tt4800000', '42', 'The Bear King', 'MV5BMTQ4MzM5MzA3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjkzNDYyNzE@', 'Red and Mulan return to help Merida uncover the truth about her father''s death.', 5, 9, '15 Nov. 2015'),
