(5591, 'tt1589021', '86', 'Flesh and Stone', 'MV5BMTg5Njk2OTI2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDE1MDU1NA@@', 'The Doctor, Amy, Dr. Song and the remaining soldiers manage to escape from the crashed ship and into the forest. The Angels attempt to create a rift in time and space much as the Doctor had found in Amy''s room when they first met. Amy meanwhile is countin', 5, 5, '1 May 2010'),
