(5616, 'tt2317659', '86', 'Dinosaurs on a Spaceship', 'MV5BMTU0MjU5MTk2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzAyMzIzMjE@', 'After a lengthy absence, the Doctor returns to Earth and scoops up up Amy and Rory for yet another adventure. He also manages somehow to include Rory''s dad, Brian Williams. Those aren''t the only travelers however as Queen Nefertiti and big-game hunter Joh', 7, 3, '8 Sep. 2012'),
(5617, 'tt2340501', '86', 'A Town Called Mercy', 'MV5BOTU2MDg0OTgxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzM5NDUzOA@@', 'The Doctor gets a Stetson (and a gun), and finds himself the reluctant Sheriff of a Western town under siege by a relentless cyborg who goes by the name of The Gunslinger. But who is he and what does he want?', 7, 4, '15 Sep. 2012'),
(5618, 'tt2399633', '86', 'The Power of Three', 'MV5BMTQxOTk5Njc1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzY1NzEzMjE@', 'Earth is suddenly visited by millions of small black cubes of unknown origin. The Doctor joins Amy, Rory and Rory''s father, Brian, to help discover what these cubes bring for humanity.', 7, 5, '22 Sep. 2012'),
(5619, 'tt2378951', '86', 'The Angels Take Manhattan', 'MV5BNjA1MzAwMDEwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTYwMTIzMjE@', 'The Doctor takes Amy and Rory to New York, where the Weeping Angels are waiting for them. River Song returns.', 7, 6, '29 Sep. 2012'),
(5620, 'tt2380513', '86', 'The Snowmen', 'MV5BMTkzNzMyODAwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMyMjIzMjE@', 'London, 1892. Snow is trying to evolve, feeding off of the nightmares of a little girl. But the Doctor has given up on saving the world. It is up to a young governess named Clara to convince him, with just one word, to save the day.', 7, 7, '25 Dec. 2012'),
(5621, 'tt2222152', '86', 'The Bells of Saint John', 'MV5BMzI3MjczNTUyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM0NDcxNDE@', 'A chance phone call reunites the Doctor with Clara in the present day. A mysterious organization, lead by the evil Miss Kizlet, sends robots known as "Spoonheads" to steal the minds of people who use the company''s WiFi. The Doctor and Clara must work toge', 7, 8, '30 Mar. 2013'),
