(5691, 'tt2562804', '87', 'Dead Reckoning', 'MV5BMjMzMDIwNDQ0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzM2MzY2MjE@', 'As Donnelly escorts Carter and Reese to their incarceration, they are ambushed, their attacker who kills Donnelly and abducts Reese. That attacker is Reese''s old and supposedly deceased ex-partner, Kara Stanton. Reese is not the first old colleague who sh', 2, 13, '31 Jan. 2013'),
(5692, 'tt2562806', '87', 'One Percent', 'MV5BMTUyMzQ5MTk3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjY1MzY2MjE@', 'The next number Reese and Finch work on is that of Logan Pierce, a self-made billionaire, whose social networking website, friendczar.com, which he founded and still operates with his best friend and partner, Justin Ogilvie, is going public in 72 hours. T', 2, 14, '7 Feb. 2013'),
(5693, 'tt2613404', '87', 'Booked Solid', 'MV5BNzc5NTI2MzU2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA1OTU2MjE@', 'Reese and Finch get jobs as a bellhop and concierge respectively at the upscale, 700 guest Coronet Hotel where the next number, Mira Dobrica, works as a maid. They figure that whatever will happen by or to Mira will happen at the hotel since she works 60 ', 2, 15, '14 Feb. 2013'),
(5694, 'tt2646630', '87', 'Relevance', 'MV5BMjExNjk5NDEzM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQ0MDY2MjE@', 'Sam Shaw and her associate Michael Cole recieve the relevant numbers from the machine, but Reese and Finch must help them, before is too late.', 2, 16, '21 Feb. 2013'),
(5695, 'tt2725454', '87', 'Proteus', 'MV5BODA4MjI2MjQwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzY3MjAyOQ@@', 'Coinciding with a storm hitting the eastern tri-state area which may require evacuation of coastal residents, the machine has not provided any numbers in three days, leading Reese and Finch to believe that there might be something wrong with it, especiall', 2, 17, '7 Mar. 2013');
