(5696, 'tt2721856', '87', 'All In', 'MV5BMjIxMzcwMDE3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDcwMjU2MjE@', 'Reese and Finch head to Atlantic City for their next number, that belonging to Lou Mitchell, an irascible, widowed and retired watch repairman, who, like many of his age, has a small electronic footprint, meaning that Reese and Finch will have to use othe', 2, 18, '14 Mar. 2013'),
(5697, 'tt2757448', '87', 'Trojan Horse', 'MV5BMTg4MTc1MDU0Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjA2NzU2MjE@', 'The next number the machine dispenses is for Monica Jacobs, a senior vice-president with Rylatech, a computer networking firm. Monica is highly regarded as a rising star in the business. She is seemingly fiercely loyal to the company, which was built from', 2, 19, '4 Apr. 2013'),
(5698, 'tt2734238', '87', 'In Extremis', 'MV5BMjIyOTYzNDA0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTI0NzU2MjE@', 'Reese first catches up with the latest number, Dr. Richard Nelson, when he is being awarded the title of professor emeritus at a lavish dinner banquet. Dr. Nelson is a well respected and renowned cardiac surgeon and researcher, with his credentials sugges', 2, 20, '25 Apr. 2013'),
(5699, 'tt2832794', '87', 'Zero Day', 'MV5BODE0OTk0MTY1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQyNTU2MjE@', 'It''s been ten days since the machine has provided a number, which means Carter has had ten days of dead bodies piling up. Finch discovers that a company called Decima is responsible for the virus which is causing these problems of inconsistency. The machi', 2, 21, '2 May 2013'),
(5700, 'tt2832792', '87', 'God Mode', 'MV5BMjE0OTYyNzUxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODMyNTU2MjE@', 'Reese and Finch team up with surprising allies in a race to save The Machine from Root and the mysterious international organization, Decima, who have both re-emerged with dangerous agendas.', 2, 22, '9 May 2013'),
(5701, 'tt2911556', '87', 'Liberty', 'MV5BNzcyNTQzMTM0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDM4NzU2MjE@', 'Nobody knows where the Machine has now relocated itself, but it is still in contact with both Finch and, by association, Reese and their new partner Shaw, as well as Root. Still institutionalized, Root may have a short term problem in dealing with her psy', 3, 1, '24 Sep. 2013'),
(5702, 'tt3092846', '87', 'Nothing to Hide', 'MV5BMTc5OTIxMDMyOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM2MDY2MjE@', 'The next number the machine dispenses is for Wayne Kruger, an Internet genius and head of a company called Life Trace, which allows people to find others through information readily available already on the web. However, Finch learns that Life Trace''s pri', 3, 2, '1 Oct. 2013'),
(5703, 'tt3146366', '87', 'Lady Killer', 'MV5BMTczMDE3MTM3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM3MzU2MjE@', 'The next number the machine dispenses is for Ian Murphy, a young man who lives off his investments. Years earlier he was a struggling college student who inherited $100,000 which he now has in a diverse portfolio of investments. Reese and Shaw initially f', 3, 3, '8 Oct. 2013'),
(5704, 'tt3106152', '87', 'Reasonable Doubt', 'MV5BMTU0MzA3MDI4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTY2NzU2MjE@', 'The next number the machine dispenses is for Vanessa Watkins, a hard-nosed prosecuting attorney who, when Finch and Reese first meet her, has just reported her husband, Jeremy Watkins, missing from their yacht. While Vanessa has put away many a criminal o', 3, 4, '15 Oct. 2013'),
(5705, 'tt3146370', '87', 'Razgovor', 'MV5BMTUzMTQ4NDgyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTI3MzU2MjE@', 'Shaw is tasked to stay close to a 10-year-old identified by The Machine, who is wanted by the Russians. Meanwhile, Carter''s mission to bring HR to justice risks exposure.', 3, 5, '22 Oct. 2013'),
(5706, 'tt3146372', '87', 'Mors Praematura', 'MV5BNzYzMjk2MTA5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTE3MzU2MjE@', 'Reese and Finch go on separate missions. Finch has noticed that Shaw has been less responsive than she even usually is and he sends Reese to go find her. Reese initially discovers evidence that Shaw was abducted, but later finds more evidence that she may', 3, 6, '29 Oct. 2013'),
(5707, 'tt3210020', '87', 'The Perfect Mark', 'MV5BMTQyNDkxOTE2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzUxMzU2MjE@', 'While Finch still keeps Root hostage, he who can''t understand why the Machine is in contact with her, he is the first to make contact with their latest number, that of hypnotherapist Hayden Price. The fact that his credentials seem made up, and that the t', 3, 7, '5 Nov. 2013'),
(5708, 'tt3227888', '87', 'Endgame', 'MV5BMTEyODk5NDE2MjheQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDM3Mjk1NjIx', 'Finch receives 38 numbers at once from the Machine. He discovers they are connected to an unknown player who is inciting an all-out war between HR and the Russian mob.', 3, 8, '12 Nov. 2013'),
(5709, 'tt3291628', '87', 'The Crossing', 'MV5BMjA5MTgzNjkzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjE3OTQ2MDE@', 'Danger closes in when the epic battle to bring the criminal organization HR to justice reaches new heights. And when the Machine suddenly gives out Reese''s number, the POI team faces their greatest threat yet.', 3, 9, '19 Nov. 2013'),
(5710, 'tt3331452', '87', 'The Devil''s Share', 'MV5BMTUxMjMxMDc4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzExNDU2MjE@', 'The team seeks justice for Carter''s murder, but Finch realizes that one person may go too far in the battle against HR. Meanwhile, NYPD officer Patrick Simmons'' number comes up.', 3, 10, '26 Nov. 2013'),
(5711, 'tt3331420', '87', 'Lethe', 'MV5BMjE0MTk0ODA4MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTg5MzU2MjE@', 'Flashbacks to Finch''s adolescence provide insight into his creation of The Machine. Also, the team receives the number of an already dying man, and Reese leaves the POI team behind in the aftermath of the war with the crime organization.', 3, 11, '17 Dec. 2013'),
(5712, 'tt3331424', '87', 'Aletheia', 'MV5BMTc1NzE1ODA4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzgyMzkyMTE@', 'Finch, Shaw and Arthur Claypool are able to escape from the clutches of Control, after which Arthur demonstrates that he has more lucid moments than he initially lets on. He informs Finch and Shaw more about Samaritan, and what from that project still exi', 3, 12, '7 Jan. 2014'),
(5713, 'tt3364202', '87', '4C', 'MV5BMTkyNTA3MjY1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTgyMzkyMTE@', 'Under the assumed name John Wiley, Reese is making his escape from his life with Finch and the Machine by taking a one-way flight to Istanbul. He is however diverted onto another flight via Rome. Initially believing it is all Finch''s doing, Reese soon lea', 3, 13, '14 Jan. 2014'),
(5714, 'tt3364208', '87', 'Provenance', 'MV5BMTkwMjExNTYyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjgyMzkyMTE@', 'Reese rejoins Finch in New York, but when the team receives the number of a highly skilled antiquities thief, a surprising turn of events finds them planning a heist which could land them all in jail.', 3, 14, '4 Feb. 2014'),
(5715, 'tt3377942', '87', 'Last Call', 'MV5BMTQ4MTM4NzAwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDgyMzkyMTE@', 'Finch goes undercover in an emergency call center to protect a 911 operator, but it soon becomes clear that the threat reaches further than the team could have anticipated.', 3, 15, '25 Feb. 2014'),
(5716, 'tt3547404', '87', 'RAM', 'MV5BMTgzNzc1NjMzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjY2NDU2MjE@', 'Some of the secrets of Finch''s operation before he enlisted the help of Reese are about to be revealed, it will also include some shocking ties to some of the stuff that has happened in present-day events.', 3, 16, '4 Mar. 2014'),
(5717, 'tt3520032', '87', '/', 'MV5BMTgzNDY1MTY0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzIwNDU2MjE@', 'The Machine tasks Root to find a janitor who has a mysterious past. However, when her presence endangers him, the Machine sends his number to Finch as well.', 3, 17, '18 Mar. 2014'),
(5718, 'tt3526628', '87', 'Allegiance', 'MV5BMTkzMzMzMjE1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDYwOTU2MjE@', 'The team gets involved in a case of international politics when a former government contractor stalks a U.N. diplomat. Meanwhile, an adversary tries to take advantage of Root.', 3, 18, '25 Mar. 2014'),
(5719, 'tt3614882', '87', 'Most Likely to...', 'MV5BMjA2MDUzNzc3MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDM0NzU2MjE@', 'Reese, Shaw and Finch are too late for their latest number, Leona Wainwright, as she is killed in front of Reese and Shaw''s eyes. They know that Leona was killed by Vigilance for information she would have had unwittingly with regard to the Machine as a f', 3, 19, '1 Apr. 2014'),
(5720, 'tt3615622', '87', 'Death Benefit', 'MV5BMTQ4MjIxMTA5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTU0NzU2MjE@', 'News of Northern Lights has hit the media, meaning that the team''s work has become more difficult if only because of the public eye on what is happening. While Shaw heads off with Root on her next assignment, Reese heads to Washington DC to reunite with F', 3, 20, '15 Apr. 2014'),
(5721, 'tt3615624', '87', 'Beta', 'MV5BNDM2MTk1NTAxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc0NzU2MjE@', 'Decima hunts down Reese and Shaw using Samaritan''s feeds. Meanwhile, Greer sets a trap for Finch by targeting his former fiancée, Grace.', 3, 21, '29 Apr. 2014'),
(5722, 'tt3615628', '87', 'A House Divided', 'MV5BMTQ3MjY3NjY4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTc0NzU2MjE@', 'Decima has completed its beta test of Samaritan and has now shut it down temporarily as Greer has to get the politicos, namely Garrison, to buy into the need to purchase it in the name of national security. Greer needs this to happen as they require the g', 3, 22, '6 May 2014'),
(5723, 'tt3615630', '87', 'Deus Ex Machina', 'MV5BMTQ0OTQ3OTE2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDc0NzU2MjE@', 'The team takes desperate action in its race to prevent Samaritan from coming online and making them its first targets. Meanwhile, the months-long battle with the anti-surveillance terrorist group Vigilance comes to a shocking conclusion.', 3, 23, '13 May 2014'),
(5724, 'tt3596112', '87', 'Panopticon', 'MV5BMTk3NzQ2NzM0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODM3MjA3MjE@', 'Required to assume new identities created by Root, the team tries to adapt to their new lives, but a new number complicates things.', 4, 1, '23 Sep. 2014'),
(5725, 'tt3897378', '87', 'Nautilus', 'MV5BMjE2NjYyMDE2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTA1NDE4MjE@', 'Harold reluctantly agrees to help John protect a young woman who is participating in a dangerous and deadly game, meanwhile Shaw works with a group of thieves as her new cover identity.', 4, 2, '30 Sep. 2014'),
(5726, 'tt3915422', '87', 'Wingman', 'MV5BMjA5MjY4NTcxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTM1NDE4MjE@', 'Finch recruits Fusco to stick close to the latest POI, a professional "wingman", but learning how to approach women soon becomes the least of his worries. Meanwhile, Reese must find a way to play by the rules at his new day job as the Machine sends Finch ', 4, 3, '7 Oct. 2014'),
(5727, 'tt3949562', '87', 'Brotherhood', 'MV5BNzczNDMyNjI4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDc3NTIwMzE@', 'The next numbers the Machine provides are for fourteen-year-old Malcolm Booker, and his eight-year-old sister, Tracie Booker, who are in foster care as their mother is incarcerated on a conviction for illegal firearms possession. Reese, who is tasked with', 4, 4, '14 Oct. 2014'),
(5728, 'tt4062328', '87', 'Prophets', 'MV5BNDQwODgyNDgxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE1NjIxMzE@', 'On Election Day Reese shoots a potential jumper and is forced to go into counseling. The new number is for a pollster who suspects the election for Governor of New York was rigged. It was - by Samaritan, and his life is now in danger.', 4, 5, '21 Oct. 2014'),
(5729, 'tt4024758', '87', 'Pretenders', 'MV5BMTU2NTA2ODQwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzE4OTcxMzE@', 'John and others try to prevent a fake detective from getting himself killed, while Harold attends a conference in Hong Kong.', 4, 6, '28 Oct. 2014'),
(5730, 'tt4069160', '87', 'Honor Among Thieves', 'MV5BMTg2ODc5NzU1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU3OTE0MzE@', 'Shaw joins a team of international thieves in order to keep tabs on the latest POI, but an unexpected turn of events puts her in danger of being detected by Samaritan. Also, Finch and Root undertake a dangerous sabotage mission.', 4, 7, '11 Nov. 2014'),
(5731, 'tt4065456', '87', 'Point of Origin', 'MV5BODc0NzA5MTIxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDk0MDA1MzE@', 'Reese volunteers as an NYPD police academy instructor in order to keep an eye on a talented young officer whose suspicious actions make him question her motives. Meanwhile, Martine, armed with information from Samaritan, hunts a member of the team.', 4, 8, '18 Nov. 2014'),
(5732, 'tt4092950', '87', 'The Devil You Know', 'MV5BNTA3MjI1MjI1NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY5OTI2MzE@', 'Reese must save Elias from the Brotherhood. He can''t get any help from Root or Shaw since Shaw''s cover is blown and Root is escorting her to underground.', 4, 9, '25 Nov. 2014'),
(5733, 'tt4092956', '87', 'The Cold War', 'MV5BMTg5Njc5NzgyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODExMDgxNDE@', 'Samaritan demonstrates its true power by taking control of New York for 48 hours and erasing crime from the city in an attempt to lure The Machine out of hiding.', 4, 10, '16 Dec. 2014'),
(5734, 'tt4128194', '87', 'If-Then-Else', 'MV5BMjE5OTQ5MDI5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzIxNDM5MzE@', 'Samaritan launches a cyber-attack on the stock exchange, leaving the team with no choice but to embark on a possible suicide mission in a desperate attempt to stop a global economic catastrophe.', 4, 11, '6 Jan. 2015'),
(5735, 'tt4159446', '87', 'Control-Alt-Delete', 'MV5BMTUzNTk4MjIyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ2ODIwNDE@', 'Control is back and begins to question the methods and intentions of Samaritan. Also, alarming news reports of a pair of vigilantes rampaging through the Northeast begin to surface.', 4, 12, '13 Jan. 2015'),
(5736, 'tt4157140', '87', 'M.I.A.', 'MV5BMTUyOTkxNTIwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI2OTMzNDE@', 'The hunt for Shaw takes Root and Reese to a small town in upstate New York where not everything is as idyllic as it seems; Fusco and a former person of interest team up.', 4, 13, '3 Feb. 2015'),
(5737, 'tt4212498', '87', 'Guilty', 'MV5BMjI5ODk1MTY3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTcyNjI0NDE@', 'While on a jury for a murder trial, Finch becomes suspicious of another juror; Reese starts to open up to a therapist.', 4, 14, '10 Feb. 2015'),
(5738, 'tt4251588', '87', 'Q & A', 'MV5BMTg0MDgxOTc5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA2NTA1NDE@', 'Reese tries to protect a software programmer with a mysterious second life, but it''s unclear which side of her life the threat is coming from. Meanwhile, Claire, a young hacker that Finch protected, reaches out to him for aid.', 4, 15, '17 Feb. 2015'),
(5739, 'tt4334116', '87', 'Blunt', 'MV5BMTc4NTg2MjcyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk4NDQ2NDE@', 'Reese and Finch must protect a street-smart grifter after her plan to steal cash from a medical marijuana dispensary fails.', 4, 16, '24 Feb. 2015'),
(5740, 'tt4364356', '87', 'Karma', 'MV5BMTcxNTg0Njc2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTAxMzY3NDE@', 'Reese and Finch try to protect a psychologist whose unorthodox methods for helping his patients find closure could cost him dearly. Meanwhile, flashbacks reveal Finch fragile state in days following bombing that killed his best friend, Nathan Ingram.', 4, 17, '10 Mar. 2015'),
(5741, 'tt4454364', '87', 'Skip', 'MV5BMjI0OTI0MDg4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTk5MTgwNTE@', 'Reese must protect a bounty hunter who refuses to let the potential threat to her life deter her from the relentless pursuit of her target. Also, Finch tries to set the plan he began in Shanghai in motion.', 4, 18, '24 Mar. 2015'),
(5742, 'tt4460310', '87', 'Search and Destroy', 'MV5BMjMwNzU2MzY2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzE4NDcyNTE@', 'Reese and Finch scramble to protect a software CEO when his behavior becomes erratic following a hacker attack that reveals all his secrets and unravels his life.', 4, 19, '7 Apr. 2015'),
(5743, 'tt4460312', '87', 'Terra Incognita', 'MV5BMTQ1MDEzNjQ1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQ5MjkzNTE@', 'Reese tries to honor Carter''s memory by solving a cold case she was unable to.', 4, 20, '14 Apr. 2015'),
(5744, 'tt4540234', '87', 'Asylum', 'MV5BMTc4NzM1NzgxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODIwOTQ1NTE@', 'Reese and Fusco get caught in the war between Elias and Dominic while Finch and Root follow a clue to Shaw''s whereabouts.', 4, 21, '28 Apr. 2015'),
(5745, 'tt4532988', '87', 'YHWH', 'MV5BNTQ1MTIyMzU0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODA1MTU2NTE@', 'Finch and Root race to save The Machine, which has been located by the rival AI, Samaritan.', 4, 22, '5 May 2015'),
