(6327, 'tt1256187', '95', 'Shelter Island', 'MV5BMjA1MTc3OTQxMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzk0OTk5MQ@@', 'Ted and Stella move up their wedding date, but the wedding may not go off as planned after Ted breaks the "No Exes Rule" and invites Robin to come in from Japan for the wedding.', 4, 5, '20 Oct. 2008'),
