(6332, 'tt1256171', '95', 'The Fight', 'MV5BMTc0MzUyOTk0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDA2OTUxMg@@', 'The guys get invited to fight alongside Doug the Bartender. However, the fight doesn''t go exactly how they imagined it to.', 4, 10, '8 Dec. 2008'),
(6333, 'tt1256172', '95', 'Little Minnesota', 'MV5BMTkzOTA2MzIyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjk3MDMyMjE@', 'Ted tries to keep his irresponsible sister from hooking up with Barney during her trip to New York, and Robin starts hanging out with Marshall at a bar for Minnesotans, not telling them that she''s really Canadian.', 4, 11, '15 Dec. 2008'),
