(6337, 'tt1256176', '95', 'The Stinsons', 'MV5BMTg2MTYyODIyOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzEyOTAzMg@@', 'The guys find out that Barney is pretending to have a wife and son to make his mother happy, but the charade is blown when Ted makes a move on Barney''s "wife."', 4, 15, '2 Mar. 2009'),
