(7397, 'tt2578788', '100', 'Goodbye Miami', 'MV5BMTQ0ODYxNzUzM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzAzNTUwMDE@', 'Having made the decision that he and Harrison will move to Argentina with Hannah, Dexter has a lot to do. He tells Deb about his plan but that doesn''t go over very well. He also tells Dr, Vogel that her son, Saxon, is dangerous and she is in need of prote', 8, 10, '8 Sep. 2013'),
