(7399, 'tt2578802', '100', 'Remember the Monsters?', 'MV5BMjA4NTg5OTU1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk5NDIxMDE@', 'Dexter has to act quickly when Hannah tells him Elway is staking out the airport. He finds a way to get him out of the way but it also leads to the entire airport being closed. With a hurricane bearing down on Miami, few options are open to them. Dexter r', 8, 12, '22 Sep. 2013'),
(7400, 'tt3731190', '101', 'Pilot', 'MV5BMTUwNjcwMTM1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODU5Mzc1MjE@', 'Student Wes Gibbins begins attending law classes taught by renowned lawyer, the tough and enigmatic Annalise Keating. She offers five students the chance to work with her, while in a flash forward, the students chosen dispose of a body.', 1, 1, '25 Sep. 2014'),
