(7406, 'tt3810436', '101', 'He Deserved to Die', 'MV5BMTYzNDE3MzcwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTk2MzQyMzE@', 'Annalise and her team throw themselves into defending Rebecca, with all sides playing dirty. Meanwhile, Michaela receives a surprising request, Laurel considers a career change, and the flash forward reveals more about Sam''s death.', 1, 7, '6 Nov. 2014'),
