(7509, 'tt3955954', '104', 'The Mole', 'MV5BODMxMzI5NjA0MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzIyNDUzMzE@', 'There''s a mole in the precinct and Holt and Jake need to find out who it is before Deputy Chief Madeline Wuntch gets wind of it. Meanwhile, Terry and Rosa visit a "silent" disco to uncover new leads for their new drug task force.', 2, 5, '2 Nov. 2014'),
(7510, 'tt4059886', '104', 'Jake and Sophia', 'MV5BMTc2MzI1MzM1NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE3MjQ0MzE@', 'Jake hits it off with a woman at a bar, but later finds out she is the attorney for a perp he is trying to put in jail. Meanwhile, Gina and Charles work to put their relationship behind them, and Amy is pressured into running for union rep.', 2, 6, '9 Nov. 2014'),
(7511, 'tt4135098', '104', 'Lockdown', 'MV5BMTQ5NTIwNzQ3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODMxMDU0MzE@', 'The precinct goes into lockdown mode on Thanksgiving night, and Jake, who was left in charge, is confident in his ability to keep spirits high and avoid chaos. Amy is less confident, as things spiral out of control.', 2, 7, '16 Nov. 2014'),
