(7552, 'tt1472901', '105', 'Legends', 'MV5BMTgzNDY3NjQyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjM4OTc3MjE@', 'Spartacus continues to train in Batiatus'' gladiatorial combat school. His tempestuous co-operation given in exchange for Batiatus'' promise to search for Sura. Meanwhile Batiatus'' money troubles and the drought continue. With the Vulcanalia approaching, Sp', 1, 3, '5 Feb. 2010'),
