(8431, 'tt2624868', '119', 'The Red Team', 'MV5BMTEwOTY5NjE0MDheQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDA1OTI1MjIx', 'Holmes discovers a man running an internet conspiracy site is dead. As he follows the chain of clues, he becomes aware of the "Red Team" and the trail leads him further down the rabbit hole than he ever imagined.', 1, 13, '31 Jan. 2013'),
(8432, 'tt2624870', '119', 'The Deductionist', 'MV5BMTU3MzUwODc3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTQ5MjUyMjE@', 'A convicted killer who is supposed to donate a kidney to his sister ends up killing the surgical staff before escaping. Holmes is forced to work with a profiler (whom he can''t stand) because she supposedly can predict what he will do next.', 1, 14, '3 Feb. 2013'),
(8433, 'tt2624872', '119', 'A Giant Gun, Filled with Drugs', 'MV5BMTYzMjUwMDkwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ5MjUyMjE@', 'Holmes'' former drug supplier comes to him for help to find his kidnapped daughter. He agrees to help him despite Watson''s protests. When Holmes appears stymied, the former dealer encourages Holmes to go back on drugs, hoping it will help him solve the cas', 1, 15, '7 Feb. 2013'),
(8434, 'tt2660926', '119', 'Details', 'MV5BMjE0NjA0NDMyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTkxOTUyMjE@', 'Detective Bell is nearly killed while driving home one night. A just-released felon is the first suspect but, when he''s killed, suspicion moves to Bell''s brother who, unlike the dedicated detective, has lived life on the wrong side of the law.', 1, 16, '14 Feb. 2013'),
(8435, 'tt2697934', '119', 'Possibility Two', 'MV5BOTAyMzAzNjM1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQ0MjYyMjE@', 'A wealthy scientist comes to Holmes with a unique case: he believes he has been "poisoned" with a genetic disorder. Holmes has to determine how a healthy person can be contaminated with a genetic disease that no one in his family has.', 1, 17, '21 Feb. 2013'),
(8436, 'tt2729080', '119', 'Déjà Vu All Over Again', 'MV5BOTQ2MTU4OTg4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDE2OTkxOQ@@', 'Watson works a case on her own about a woman who has disappeared while Holmes deals with a subway murder. As they work their separate cases they gradually appear to be connected, even though they can''t determine exactly how.', 1, 18, '14 Mar. 2013'),
(8437, 'tt2733692', '119', 'Snow Angels', 'MV5BMTU5MDcxNzg1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDQzNTIzOQ@@', 'In the middle of a winter storm, Holmes and Watson must solve the murder of a guard during a botched robbery and unravel the killer''s true plan. The pair also get an interesting new roommate.', 1, 19, '4 Apr. 2013'),
(8438, 'tt2778808', '119', 'Dead Man''s Switch', 'MV5BMTA3NDkyMjc3NjJeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDczNTU1MjIx', 'A blackmailer uses tapes of underage girls to get money from their fathers. When Holmes witnesses the blackmailer''s murder, it becomes a race to find out who his accomplice is and prevent the videos from being released on the Internet.', 1, 20, '25 Apr. 2013'),
(8439, 'tt2778806', '119', 'A Landmark Story', 'MV5BMjIyMjQwMjk0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI1NTUyMjE@', 'A man connected to the classification of a valuable building as a landmark trust dies when his pacemaker is deliberately short circuited. Holmes soon learns the one behind the murder is an old nemesis known to him only as "Moriarty".', 1, 21, '2 May 2013'),
(8440, 'tt2778816', '119', 'Risk Management', 'MV5BMTk0NTI2OTMyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODIzMTg0OQ@@', 'Moriarty asks Holmes to find out who murdered a mechanic in Brooklyn. Despite Watson''s protests, Holmes thinks this case will help him uncover Moriarty''s true identity, but it will, in fact, lead Holmes to something much worse.', 1, 22, '9 May 2013'),
(8441, 'tt2767596', '119', 'The Woman', 'MV5BMTY5NDcwMTM5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTE2MTYyMjE@', 'Holmes reconnects with Irene, his one true love that he thought had been taken from him by Moriarity. He tries to protect her as she recovers from her trauma but he soon learns that it isn''t she that needs protection.', 1, 23, '16 May 2013'),
(8442, 'tt2767598', '119', 'Heroine', 'MV5BMjA0ODEyMzAxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjA0OTE1OQ@@', 'While recovering from his gun shot wounds, Holmes eschews painkillers while working on a case of a Greek shipping magnate - involving an assassination and currency manipulation - before his final showdown with Moriarty.', 1, 24, '16 May 2013'),
(8443, 'tt2801436', '119', 'Step Nine', 'MV5BMTgyNTc5ODg2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODYyNzgxMDE@', 'Holmes and Watson travel to London to help track down an old mentor and investigate an unsolved mystery. Rhys Ifans guest stars.', 2, 1, '26 Sep. 2013'),
(8444, 'tt3125780', '119', 'Solve for X', 'MV5BMTY1MTA2Nzc4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY2NzUyMjE@', 'When a well-respected mathematician is found dead, Holmes and Watson set out to solve a murder and the purpose of the highly guarded equation he was trying to decipher.', 2, 2, '3 Oct. 2013'),
(8445, 'tt3093706', '119', 'We Are Everyone', 'MV5BMjAyMDA4NjE1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODIxMjkyMDE@', 'When Holmes and Watson set out to track down a civil contractor who leaked classified information, their lives are disrupted when they are targeted by the group of cyber-activists protecting him. Tony Award Winner Steve Kazee guest stars.', 2, 3, '10 Oct. 2013'),
(8446, 'tt3182700', '119', 'Poison Pen', 'MV5BMTQ1NjE0MTkyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzEwNDYzMDE@', 'A dominatrix finds her client dead in S&M gear. When poison is revealed to be the cause of death, the nanny becomes a suspect.', 2, 4, '17 Oct. 2013'),
(8447, 'tt3255194', '119', 'Ancient History', 'MV5BNTc3OTgxMzMyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ3MjYyMjE@', 'Holmes and Watson find themselves digging through the dark world of the mob to find a killer when they discover the body of a former assassin.', 2, 5, '24 Oct. 2013'),
(8448, 'tt3182708', '119', 'An Unnatural Arrangement', 'MV5BMjIyNTM2ODU3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE0MTYyMjE@', 'Captain Gregson''s team learns a bit about his personal life after his home is invaded. Holmes and Watson track the gunman.', 2, 6, '31 Oct. 2013'),
(8449, 'tt3182732', '119', 'The Marchioness', 'MV5BMTcxOTE3MTgzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTUwMzY1MDE@', 'Sherlock''s brother, Mycroft, arrives in New York and enlists Holmes and Watson to help solve a case involving his former fiancee. Meanwhile, Sherlock has a difficult time accepting Mycroft and Joan''s relationship. Rhys Ifans guest stars.', 2, 7, '7 Nov. 2013'),
(8450, 'tt3295662', '119', 'Blood Is Thicker', 'MV5BNzEwMDI5ODM5Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkzODUyMjE@', 'When a beautiful young woman is murdered, Holmes and Watson investigate her ties to a billionaire CEO. Meanwhile, Mycroft makes a case for Sherlock to move back to London.', 2, 8, '14 Nov. 2013'),
(8451, 'tt3317624', '119', 'On the Line', 'MV5BMjE5NzgyMDU5Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDk5MzYyMjE@', 'Holmes and Watson uncover the identity of a serial killer whose case has gone cold and find themselves butting heads with the NYPD.', 2, 9, '21 Nov. 2013'),
(8452, 'tt3347990', '119', 'Tremors', 'MV5BMTU3NTQ4MjA0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA4MjYyMjE@', 'When an investigation goes horribly wrong, Sherlock must testify in an official police inquiry which jeopardizes his and Watson''s future with the NYPD.', 2, 10, '5 Dec. 2013'),
(8453, 'tt3357010', '119', 'Internal Audit', 'MV5BMjAxMDY1ODM3OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTMyNTc3MDE@', 'When a hedge fund manager who was also running a Ponzi scheme is murdered, Holmes and Watson must determine which of his clients is guilty. Also, Sherlock contemplates sponsoring a fellow recovering addict.', 2, 11, '12 Dec. 2013'),
(8454, 'tt3392730', '119', 'The Diabolical Kind', 'MV5BMTQ3MTcxMTQwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDg2MzYyMjE@', 'Holmes and Watson come face to face with Moriarty when their one-time adversary is brought in as a consultant on a kidnapping case. Meanwhile, Detective Bell continues his struggle on the road to recovery. Natalie Dormer Returns as Moriarty.', 2, 12, '2 Jan. 2014');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `imdb_id`, `serie_id`, `title`, `poster_id`, `summary`, `season`, `episode`, `air_date`) VALUES
(8455, 'tt3415320', '119', 'All in the Family', 'MV5BMTYyNjU4Nzk4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU3MTI5MDE@', 'When a body is found in a barrel, Holmes and Watson launch an investigation into the mafia''s ties to the murder. Meanwhile, Sherlock attempts to make amends with Detective Bell. Peter Gerety and Paul Sorvino guest star.', 2, 13, '9 Jan. 2014'),
(8456, 'tt3459420', '119', 'Dead Clade Walking', 'MV5BNDc1NDE0ODE2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTE3MDYwMTE@', 'When Joan revisits one of Sherlock''s cold cases, she discovers an unsolved murder is connected to a rare prehistoric fossil. Meanwhile, Sherlock finds himself in uncharted territory when his duties as a sobriety sponsor cross his personal boundaries.', 2, 14, '30 Jan. 2014'),
(8457, 'tt3479240', '119', 'Corpse De Ballet', 'MV5BNzY3NDU0OTM2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA5MjMxMTE@', 'Holmes'' latest investigation takes him inside a professional dance company when an up-and-coming ballerina is murdered. Meanwhile, Watson embarks on a solo enquiry to find a homeless veteran when his friend alleges he was abducted.', 2, 15, '6 Feb. 2014'),
(8458, 'tt3505070', '119', 'The One Percent Solution', 'MV5BMTE0MDM0NTY5NzVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDA4ODM1MjIx', 'Tensions rise when Holmes and Watson are forced to partner with Gareth Lestrade, Sherlock''s former Scotland Yard colleague, on a bombing investigation.', 2, 16, '27 Feb. 2014'),
(8459, 'tt3505072', '119', 'Ears to You', 'MV5BNDQwMDQwMzI1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg5MzMzMTE@', 'Holmes and Watson consult on a case in which a man suspected of murdering his wife years ago receives a ransom demand for her safe return. Meanwhile, Lestrade overstays his welcome at the brownstone and seems unwilling to leave.', 2, 17, '6 Mar. 2014'),
(8460, 'tt3505076', '119', 'The Hound of the Cancer Cells', 'MV5BMjMxMzc0NzYzM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTE1MjgzMTE@', 'When a famous cancer researcher is found dead, Holmes and Watson must determine if the scientist''s untimely demise was tied to his latest cutting-edge invention. Meanwhile, Bell is finally cleared to re-enter the field.', 2, 18, '13 Mar. 2014'),
(8461, 'tt3575976', '119', 'The Many Mouths of Andrew Colville', 'MV5BMTc2OTY4NDM2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDA3MDg0MTE@', 'A serial killer known for biting his victims appears to be killing again, even though he was presumed dead.', 2, 19, '3 Apr. 2014'),
(8462, 'tt3602686', '119', 'No Lack of Void', 'MV5BMTg3NjkyNjA4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjcyNTI1MTE@', 'Holmes and Watson must find the source of anthrax that may be used for a terrorist attack.', 2, 20, '10 Apr. 2014'),
(8463, 'tt3602688', '119', 'The Man with the Twisted Lip', 'MV5BMTU4NTc3ODE2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTU3MTU2MTE@', 'When Sherlock''s brother Mycroft makes a surprise return to New York, his motivations cause discord between Sherlock and Joan. Meanwhile, a missing person case takes Sherlock and Joan inside the world of unmanned aeronautics.', 2, 21, '24 Apr. 2014'),
(8464, 'tt3668096', '119', 'Paint It Black', 'MV5BMTU4NDI5NzI0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY2MTU2MTE@', 'With Watson kidnapped, the Holmes brothers are extorted to buy her back by acquiring something the gangsters greatly value. As the clock runs down on Watson''s life, Sherlock is forced to work with his despised brother Mycroft.', 2, 22, '1 May 2014'),
(8465, 'tt3668094', '119', 'Art in the Blood', 'MV5BNjEyMTAxMjQ1Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTc4MjU3MTE@', 'Mycroft''s handler at MI6 asks Sherlock to investigate the death of a mentally disturbed operative. Watson tries to cope with her feelings about the kidnapping, as well as Mycroft''s deceptions.', 2, 23, '8 May 2014'),
(8466, 'tt3611988', '119', 'The Grand Experiment', 'MV5BMTQ2ODY4MjQ1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY4MjU3MTE@', 'Rising tension between Sherlock and Watson bring their partnership to a crossroads, but they endeavor to put their differences aside while they help Sherlock''s brother, Mycroft, who faces accusations of treason and murder. Rhys Ifans returns as Mycroft Ho', 2, 24, '15 May 2014'),
(8467, 'tt3596108', '119', 'Enough Nemesis to Go Around', 'MV5BMjMyNDcxNjM3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODYyODc5MjE@', 'Holmes returns to New York with a new apprentice and a renewed interest in working with the NYPD after being fired by London''s MI6. Unfortunately, Joan, the NYPD''s new go-to PI, must give her approval first.', 3, 1, '30 Oct. 2014'),
(8468, 'tt4038658', '119', 'The Five Orange Pipz', 'MV5BMjM1MDM0NDIzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjczMDUyMzE@', 'When Holmes and Watson join forces on a double homicide, Sherlock''s new apprentice, Kitty, threatens the investigation when she allows her jealousy of Sherlock and Joan''s work rapport to override her better judgment.', 3, 2, '6 Nov. 2014'),
(8469, 'tt4166616', '119', 'Just a Regular Irregular', 'MV5BNTM0NDIxMDU1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA4MzM0MzE@', 'Sherlock helps a math genius from his network of "Irregulars" experts after he stumbles upon a body while participating in a math puzzle competition. Meanwhile, Joan attempts to extend an olive branch after she learns about Kitty''s past.', 3, 3, '13 Nov. 2014'),
(8470, 'tt4109322', '119', 'Bella', 'MV5BMTcwOTcyNjc2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU5ODE0MzE@', 'An A.I. computer is suspected for the murder of its creator; Sherlock and the team go to work to solve the case.', 3, 4, '20 Nov. 2014'),
(8471, 'tt4188090', '119', 'Rip Off', 'MV5BMTEzMjM0MjE0NDNeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDUwNjg0NDMx', 'A man''s hand is found in the streets. Sherlock and his new protégé investigate to find the rest of the body. Meanwhile Sherlock finds Watson''s book written about him.', 3, 5, '27 Nov. 2014'),
(8472, 'tt4193778', '119', 'Terra Pericolosa', 'MV5BNTI4MTA2MjM1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMyNDI2MzE@', 'Holmes and Watson search for a thief who committed murder to steal a rare map. Meanwhile, Watson becomes concerned with Sherlock''s escalating interference into Kitty''s burgeoning personal life. Mamie Gummer guest stars.', 3, 6, '4 Dec. 2014'),
(8473, 'tt4132718', '119', 'The Adventure of the Nutmeg Concoction', 'MV5BNDIzOTQyMDk3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjExMzc2MzE@', 'A bored Sherlock forces his investigative services onto Joan, who is trying to locate a woman who has been missing for five years, and the only clue is the smell of nutmeg at the site of her disappearance. Meanwhile, Joan''s bond with her long-distance boy', 3, 7, '11 Dec. 2014'),
(8474, 'tt4259236', '119', 'End of Watch', 'MV5BMTQ1MTczMjEyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE5MTQ3MzE@', 'Holmes and Watson join forces with the NYPD after a police officer is murdered. Also, Sherlock searches for the creator of a "recovery blog" who is posting personal statements he has made in sobriety meetings.', 3, 8, '18 Dec. 2014'),
(8475, 'tt4165846', '119', 'The Eternity Injection', 'MV5BMjQwODQ4MTg4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQ0MzQ5MzE@', 'When a nurse Watson used to work with asks for her help finding their missing acquaintance, the woman''s trail leads Watson and Holmes to another person who has disappeared. Also, Sherlock struggles with his sobriety when he finds the recovery process mono', 3, 9, '8 Jan. 2015'),
(8476, 'tt4300564', '119', 'Seed Money', 'MV5BNTgwNjcyNjMyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzE1OTUwNDE@', 'While Kitty tries to find a runaway teen, Sherlock and Joan work a case in which the murder of a brilliant bioengineer looks to be at the hands of a drug cartel. Also, Joan makes a major life decision but worries it will impact Sherlock negatively, not kn', 3, 10, '15 Jan. 2015'),
(8477, 'tt4300570', '119', 'The Illustrious Client', 'MV5BMjEyMDUxNjc0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDc1NjUxNDE@', 'Watson starts her new job as an investigator for an insurance firm, but ends up joining forces on a case with Sherlock when a threat to Kitty emerges.', 3, 11, '22 Jan. 2015'),
(8478, 'tt4214936', '119', 'The One That Got Away', 'MV5BMTY3ODU3OTcyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDI2MjcyNDE@', 'As Kitty begins to unravel due to the imminent threat to her safety, Sherlock and Joan intensify their efforts to help her. Also, the origin of Sherlock and Kitty''s relationship is revealed.', 3, 12, '29 Jan. 2015'),
(8479, 'tt4389654', '119', 'Hemlock', 'MV5BMTA3OTkyOTEwMjNeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDYxMTk2MzQx', 'Holmes and Watson are faced with a very large suspect pool when a debt collector is murdered; Andrew wants Watson to meet his father.', 3, 13, '5 Feb. 2015'),
(8480, 'tt4389658', '119', 'The Female of the Species', 'MV5BMTQ3NjgwODQwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDAyNzQ0NDE@', 'Sherlock and Detective Bell investigate the kidnapping of two zebras from the zoo.', 3, 14, '12 Feb. 2015'),
(8481, 'tt4331982', '119', 'When Your Number''s Up', 'MV5BMjA4MzU1OTAzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDk1NzY1NDE@', 'Holmes and Watson follow a blood trail into the world of wrongful death compensation when they investigate a series of murders in which the killer leaves envelopes of cash on the victims. Also, Holmes makes a generous gesture towards Watson as she suffers', 3, 15, '19 Feb. 2015'),
(8482, 'tt4454588', '119', 'For All You Know', 'MV5BMTkyODY4ODc2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI4MjE3NDE@', 'Holmes investigates himself when he becomes a suspect in a murder that took place during the height of his addiction; clues make Holmes question his innocence.', 3, 16, '5 Mar. 2015'),
(8483, 'tt4472348', '119', 'T-Bone and the Iceman', 'MV5BMjAwOTQ1MzcwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTEzNDQ4NDE@', 'A murder victim turns out to have been instantly frozen at the time of death; Watson is forced to have an awkward conversation with her brother after learning he is having an affair.', 3, 17, '12 Mar. 2015'),
(8484, 'tt4525072', '119', 'The View from Olympus', 'MV5BMjI5MDU4NzcxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ2MDUxNTE@', 'A driver for a ride sharing company is intentionally run over by a city cab, Sherlock and Joan wonder if it''s a case of professional jealousy. A romance Sherlock has with a longtime Irregular complicates when she makes a shocking request.', 3, 18, '2 Apr. 2015'),
(8485, 'tt4483404', '119', 'One Watson, One Holmes', 'MV5BMjI0NzgzODk5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTgxNzYyNTE@', 'Holmes and Watson are drawn into an Internet war when a member of the everyone hacker group is murdered.', 3, 19, '9 Apr. 2015'),
(8486, 'tt4532492', '119', 'A Stitch in Time', 'MV5BMTYzMTM2ODYyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjY1MjkzNTE@', 'Holmes and Watson investigate the murder of a professional skeptic, a man who debunked paranormal, religious and scientific phenomenon for a living. The case becomes urgent when his homicide reveals a potential threat to homeland security. Also, Captain G', 3, 20, '16 Apr. 2015'),
(8487, 'tt4562958', '119', 'Under My Skin', 'MV5BMTg2MDExMTA4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg0NDY0NTE@', 'Two New York City paramedics are shot and their ambulance with its patient is abducted by the murderer. Holmes and Watson join the manhunt to find out what happened and why. Holmes learns information about Alfredo, which strains their relationship.', 3, 21, '23 Apr. 2015'),
(8488, 'tt4599456', '119', 'The Best Way Out Is Always Through', 'MV5BNjU1NDM0MTkwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTczMzY1NTE@', 'When a judge is murdered, Holmes and Watson become involved in the interstate search to find the prime suspect, an escaped convict from a privatized prison. Also, when Holmes applies his deductive reasoning to Detective Bell''s new relationship, the romanc', 3, 22, '30 Apr. 2015'),
(8489, 'tt4599458', '119', 'Absconded', 'MV5BMjE0ODc4MzQ5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDg1ODQ2NTE@', 'A researcher - one of Sherlock''s fellow beekeepers - who was investigating a deadly honeybee outbreak is killed; Capt. Gregson asks Watson for help with an unofficial investigation that helps him make a decision.', 3, 23, '7 May 2015'),
(8490, 'tt4599460', '119', 'A Controlled Descent', 'MV5BMjMxMjAyNzg1Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI2MTk2NTE@', 'Holmes and Watson take on an investigation of a personal nature when Holmes'' friend and former recovery sponsor Alfredo suddenly disappears.', 3, 24, '14 May 2015'),
(8491, 'tt4764456', '119', 'The Past Is Parent', 'MV5BMTUwOTE2Mjc0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzkzNjYyNzE@', 'Sherlock faces the consequences of his relapse, and his father arrives to try to fix the situation. Joan and Sherlock, trying to get back on NYPD''s good side, search for a missing woman working the theory she was killed by her husband.', 4, 1, '5 Nov. 2015'),
(8492, 'tt4864802', '119', 'Evidence of Things Not Seen', 'MV5BMjE3ODgyOTUyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDE0ODYyNzE@', 'When Morland offers to use his influence to have Sherlock and Joan reinstated as consultants to the NYPD, Sherlock''s mistrust of his father makes him question his motivation to help. Also, with no work offers coming in, Watson wrangles a gig with the FBI ', 4, 2, '12 Nov. 2015'),
(8493, 'tt4977670', '119', 'Tag, You''re Me', 'MV5BNTE0ODMzNDI5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI0NjYyNzE@', 'Sherlock and Watson are back working with the NYPD on a double homicide involving a doppelganger of the intended victim. Sherlock offers his consulting services to his father, to help him finish his business in New York.', 4, 3, '19 Nov. 2015'),
(8494, 'tt4962286', '119', 'All My Exes Live in Essex', 'MV5BMjEyNDgyNzcwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ2NzUzNzE@', 'When Holmes and Watson investigate the murder of a fertility lab technician, they discover the woman had a secret personal life that leads them to multiple suspects. Also, the tables are turned on Watson when she''s investigated by an NYPD detective.', 4, 4, '26 Nov. 2015'),
(8495, 'tt5205008', '119', 'The Games Underfoot', 'MV5BMTk2Njg4NDE4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ1NjY0NzE@', 'Sherlock and Joan investigate the murder of a struggling archaeologist who was seemingly killed for some vintage video games he unearthed.', 4, 5, '10 Dec. 2015'),
(8496, 'tt5128632', '119', 'The Cost of Doing Business', 'MV5BMTU1NDIzNTk2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTUxODE1NzE@', 'Morland offers to act as one of his son''s "Irregular" consultants so that he can lend Sherlock and Joan his considerable resources to help them solve a case.', 4, 6, '17 Dec. 2015'),
(8497, 'tt5266828', '119', 'Miss Taken', 'MV5BMTg3OTc5ODU3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzUwNzY2NzE@', 'The duo goes against a clever opponent, who forces Holmes to think out of the box. Meanwhile Watson''s troubles with her father are brought into focus when he writes a book about her and Holmes.', 4, 7, '7 Jan. 2016'),
