(8908, 'tt0588155', '125', 'Just Like Gwen and Gavin', 'MV5BMTUwMzAxMDU3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzY1ODM0MjE@', 'Hetting an education: Taylor Doose learns the Winter Carnival can be success without him. Paris learns the Yale Daily News staff loathes and fears her. And Lorelai learns Luke has a daughter.', 6, 12, '17 Jan. 2006'),
(8909, 'tt0588142', '125', 'Friday Night''s Alright for Fighting', 'MV5BMjA4NzQ5NDExNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODg0ODM0MjE@', 'Lorelai and Rory go to the Gilmore mansion for Friday night dinner, and there is a fight. Luke is still getting to know April.', 6, 13, '31 Jan. 2006'),
