(8924, 'tt0868143', '125', 'Go, Bulldogs!', 'MV5BMjE2NDE3MDgyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA4NzM0MjE@', 'Christopher talks Lorelai into visiting Rory at Yale during Parents'' Weekend, and Lorelai is surprised to find that Richard and Emily are also there. Trying to prove how cool he is, Christopher invites all of Rory''s co-workers on the Yale Daily News to an', 7, 6, '7 Nov. 2006'),
