(9192, 'tt1615662', '128', 'The Good News', 'MV5BODA3OTE4Mjc4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDUxODczMjE@', 'Don flies to Los Angeles to visit Anna before his New Year''s vacation to Acapulco, but her bad news influences him to cancel his vacation and return to New York, where he discovers that Lane has problems of his own.', 4, 3, '8 Aug. 2010'),
