(10172, 'tt0584128', '140', 'Designing Mothers', 'MV5BMTQ2MTcxNjE1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY3Njg3MjE@', 'Danny meets Vicki''s mother, an interior designer, who redecorates Stephanie and Michelle''s room without consulting him and it leads he and Vicki to argue and break up.', 6, 11, '8 Dec. 1992'),
(10173, 'tt0776056', '140', 'A Very Tanner Christmas', 'MV5BMTQ0OTYxOTUyOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMDg3MjE@', 'While Michelle and Stephanie are busy making extra long Christmas lists, other members of the Tanner household are not feeling so cheery. Danny misses Vicki, Rebecca misses the white Christmases of her childhood, and DJ worries that she will miss Steve af', 6, 12, '15 Dec. 1992'),
(10174, 'tt0584215', '140', 'The Dating Game', 'MV5BMjIyNTE2NTI5NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI2Njg3MjE@', 'Both Joey and Stephanie try to turn friendly dinners into romantic first dates: Josh takes Stephanie out for pizza, and Joey invites his boss, Alison, to the house for dinner. (Original Broadcast: Season 6, Episode 13)', 6, 13, '5 Jan. 1993'),
(10175, 'tt0776059', '140', 'Birthday Blues', 'MV5BMTg3NDM2NDM2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTMxMDg3MjE@', 'D.J. is planning she and Steve''s 6 month anniversary and is horrified to learn she''s forgotten Kimmy''s 16th birthday is on the same day. Frantically, she scrambles to get the family together to throw a last-minute party for Kimmy.', 6, 14, '19 Jan. 1993'),
(10176, 'tt0584106', '140', 'Be True to Your Pre-School', 'MV5BMTUxMDQyNDkwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDI3Njg3MjE@', 'Jesse lies about the twins'' academic abilities to get them in to a prestigious preschool. Kimmy gets her drivers license.', 6, 15, '26 Jan. 1993'),
(10177, 'tt0776000', '140', 'The Heartbreak Kid', 'MV5BMTczOTY0NjIzNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY5OTc3MjE@', 'Michelle mistakes Steve''s friendliness for romantic love. Jesse has trouble with his new computer.', 6, 16, '9 Feb. 1993'),
(10178, 'tt0584199', '140', 'Silence Is Not Golden', 'MV5BNjU3MzA0Mzc4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTg1Njg3MjE@', 'When Stephanie is paired with a classmate she hates for a school project, she finds out that the boy''s father is beating him, and is sworn to secrecy.', 6, 17, '16 Feb. 1993'),
(10179, 'tt0776071', '140', 'Please Don''t Touch the Dinosaur', 'MV5BMjMxNjU1MzMyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMxMDg3MjE@', 'Jesse and Danny both get volunteered to take Michelle''s class on a field trip to the museum. Jesse''s rowdier bunch of kids cause trouble and end up destroying a dinosaur skeleton. Meanwhile, Stephanie and D.J. get into an argument over who owns a baseball', 6, 18, '23 Feb. 1993'),
(10180, 'tt0584206', '140', 'Subterranean Graduation Blues', 'MV5BMTQ0NzM0ODE2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjE2Njg3MjE@', 'Jesse is determined to show up everybody who doubted he could finish high school; but on the night of the graduation, everybody gets delayed when the subway train gets stuck.', 6, 19, '2 Mar. 1993'),
(10181, 'tt0584144', '140', 'Grand Gift Auto', 'MV5BMjA4NTA1MjYxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjI4Njg3MjE@', 'Joey gets D.J. a car for her birthday, but the police show up with the news it''s stolen and suspect Joey of being the thief. When the Tanners attempt to prove his innocence, Joey gets the impression that he''s not appreciated in the family.', 6, 20, '16 Mar. 1993'),
(10182, 'tt0584195', '140', 'Room for One More', 'MV5BMjE0NzE5NDQ2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODk1Njg3MjE@', 'Jesse discusses with Becky the possibility of having another baby, but he finds out he already has his hands full when one of the twins is sick, Joey''s injured and Danny and the kids help with the radio show run from home while baby-sitting a neighbor''s p', 6, 21, '6 Apr. 1993'),
(10183, 'tt0584192', '140', 'Prom Night', 'MV5BMTQxMzI1NTQ1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDM1Njg3MjE@', 'As DJ prepares for prom, she fears that Steve may have resurfacing feelings for his old girlfriend, Rachel. On the big night, DJ realizes that her suspicions may be accurate, as Rachel tries to get Steve to escort her to an after-party at the hotel. Meanw', 6, 22, '4 May 1993'),
(10184, 'tt0584221', '140', 'The House Meets the Mouse: Part 1', 'MV5BMTU3MTc1OTk0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTk1Njg3MjE@', 'The family takes a trip to Disney World, where they each encounter their own form of disaster: Danny cannot propose to Vicky without being interrupted; Jesse and Joey do a radio broadcast live from the bottom of a shark tank; Michelle gets to be princess ', 6, 23, '11 May 1993'),
(10185, 'tt0584222', '140', 'The House Meets the Mouse: Part 2', 'MV5BMTU0NTg4MTA4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE2Njg3MjE@', 'After Michelle runs away from DJ, Stephanie, and Kimmy when they get frustrated with her bossiness, the girls become frantic. Meanwhile, Rebecca gets fed up with Jesse, who continues to spend all of his time away from the family; and Danny struggles to fi', 6, 24, '18 May 1993'),
(10186, 'tt0763161', '140', 'It Was a Dark and Stormy Night', 'MV5BMTUwODk0NjYxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzY0Mjg3MjE@', 'DJ, Stephanie and Michelle come home from summer camp. Michelle brings home a rabbit she was supposed to let go, but as Danny says he should be let go, DJ, Stephanie and Michelle go back to camp with Steve and let the rabbit go. When they get there they f', 7, 1, '14 Sep. 1993'),
(10187, 'tt0775999', '140', 'The Apartment', 'MV5BOTIyNTY5NjYwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjU5OTc3MjE@', 'Steve gets an apartment and D.J goes for a visit. She falls asleep on the couch and Danny gets angry when she doesn''t come home on time. He goes to the building and looks through the window.', 7, 2, '21 Sep. 1993'),
(10188, 'tt0776077', '140', 'Wrong-Way Tanner', 'MV5BMTkzMzI0OTUyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzUxMDg3MjE@', 'While her skills are questionable, Michelle is having lots of fun playing on the soccer team- until she scores the winning goal for the other team. Meanwhile, Stephanie catches everyone''s most embarrassing moments on her video camera.', 7, 3, '28 Sep. 1993'),
(10189, 'tt0776074', '140', 'Tough Love', 'MV5BMTkxNTQ3MDQ3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzUxMDg3MjE@', 'Nicky and Alexander''s behavior gets out of hand when Becky and Jesse can''t bring themselves to discipline them; when Jesse finally puts his foot down he starts to regret it after the boys call him ''mean daddy''.', 7, 4, '5 Oct. 1993'),
(10190, 'tt0584135', '140', 'Fast Friends', 'MV5BMTYwMTgzMjMzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI3MzE1NTE@', 'Stephanie meets new friends, but soon feels pressured to smoke. Jesse and Joey host a radio show called Teen Talk; or is it Yakkin'' With Youth?', 7, 5, '12 Oct. 1993'),
(10191, 'tt0584201', '140', 'Smash Club: the Next Generation', 'MV5BMjI4MTE1NjA2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY1Njg3MjE@', 'Jesse is surprised to learn that he has inherited an old night club where his band used to play. But he soon learns that reopening the run-down building for a new generation takes more than just good ideas.', 7, 6, '19 Oct. 1993');
