(10192, 'tt0584150', '140', 'High Anxiety', 'MV5BMTQxNzA2MzIwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ3Njg3MjE@', 'Michelle wants Danny to stop treating her like a baby. Jesse can''t make decisions about the renovation of his club.', 7, 7, '26 Oct. 1993'),
(10193, 'tt0584101', '140', 'Another Opening, Another No Show', 'MV5BOTE4MDIxNjYzNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI3Njg3MjE@', 'The Smash Club is about to open, but everything that can go wrong does; Joey books the wrong band, Kimmy gives her waitress uniform a "creative" touch, and no one can find the owner- Jesse.', 7, 8, '2 Nov. 1993'),
(10194, 'tt0584216', '140', 'The Day of the Rhino', 'MV5BNDAxODQ2MTcwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTM2Njg3MjE@', 'Michelle and her friends get ripped off after sending in their money for giant plush Rigby rhino dolls and confront Rigby during a public appearance at the mall. Vicki and Becky teach D.J. a lesson how guys will say anything to compliment women''s appearan', 7, 9, '9 Nov. 1993'),
(10195, 'tt0584231', '140', 'The Prying Game', 'MV5BMjE2OTMwNjcyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjA2Njg3MjE@', 'Stephanie and Kimmy resort to snooping around Steve''s apartment when they suspect that he''s cheating on DJ with another girl. Meanwhile, Jesse, Joey, and Danny tape an infomercial to sell a hair care accessory that Jesse invented, which ends in chaos.', 7, 10, '16 Nov. 1993'),
(10196, 'tt0584213', '140', 'The Bicycle Thief', 'MV5BNTExOTkwMjY3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjM2Njg3MjE@', 'When Michelle''s bike is stolen, everyone sets out on a search to find it. Unfortunately, they recover three bikes, non of which are Michelle''s. To make matters worse, the family realizes they have now stolen these bikes- and the local crime stoppers group', 7, 11, '23 Nov. 1993'),
(10197, 'tt0584208', '140', 'Support Your Local Parents', 'MV5BMjAwNzM3MjE2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTI2Njg3MjE@', 'Jesse and Becky are concerned that Nicky and Alex won''t socialize with other kids, and attend a parent support group. In the meantime, Stephanie and Michelle learn D.J. has received a traffic ticket and request full access to her wardrobe or they''ll tell ', 7, 12, '30 Nov. 1993'),
(10198, 'tt0584228', '140', 'The Perfect Couple', 'MV5BMTg3MDY3MjIxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODM2Njg3MjE@', 'Joey has been hired as the host for a test-run of a new game show called The Perfect Couple, which tests couples at different stages in their relationships, to see how well they know each other. DJ and Steve are the "dating couple", Danny and Vicki are th', 7, 13, '14 Dec. 1993'),
(10199, 'tt0584153', '140', 'Is It True About Stephanie?', 'MV5BNDQzMTUyNjcxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjE4Njg3MjE@', 'After Stephanie makes a date with Gia''s crush, Gia spreads a nasty rumor, prompting Stephanie to fight back with a prank of her own. Meanwhile, Danny''s behavior after his break up with Vicki makes the rest of the family wonder if he''s cracking up.', 7, 14, '4 Jan. 1994'),
(10200, 'tt0584235', '140', 'The Test', 'MV5BMTYzNTE3NTQwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc2Njg3MjE@', 'D.J. stresses out over taking the S.A.Ts, despite her family''s reassurances that ''it''s just a test''.', 7, 15, '11 Jan. 1994'),
(10201, 'tt0584158', '140', 'Joey''s Funny Valentine', 'MV5BNDI0NTExMjg0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTU1Njg3MjE@', 'Joey thinks he has found his dream girl, comic Roxy Mardin, But she turns out to be a nightmare.', 7, 16, '25 Jan. 1994'),
(10202, 'tt0584225', '140', 'The Last Dance', 'MV5BMjI3NDQzODQzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ2Njg3MjE@', 'During his visit to San Francisco, Jesse''s beloved grandfather, Papouli, dies in his sleep. Jesse and Michelle are both devastated as they try to come to terms with his death.', 7, 17, '8 Feb. 1994'),
(10203, 'tt0584162', '140', 'Kissing Cousins', 'MV5BMTAyNTQzNTQ0NjleQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDk3NTY4NzIx', 'Jesse''s cousin Stavros comes to visit and takes advantage of the whole family.', 7, 18, '15 Feb. 1994'),
(10204, 'tt0584166', '140', 'Love on the Rocks', 'MV5BNDQyMDM3MDA1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ1Njg3MjE@', 'When she starts hanging out with Kimmy and her new boyfriend (who can''t keep their hands off of each other), DJ realizes that she and Steve have really cooled off. So when Steve goes on a class trip to Los Angeles, DJ contemplates whether or not the two o', 7, 19, '1 Mar. 1994'),
(10205, 'tt0584176', '140', 'Michelle a la Cart', '01', 'Michelle is excited about building a go-cart with Aunt Becky, but gets discouraged when she hears her dad & Uncle Jesse teasing Becky. Stephanie shows Joey some ballet moves. DJ and Steve deal with the fact that they are no longer a couple.', 7, 20, '15 Mar. 1994'),
(10206, 'tt0584107', '140', 'Be Your Own Best Friend', 'MV5BNjg4MDAxODE5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDY3Njg3MjE@', 'Danny suggests Michelle''s class do a project of drawing their best friend. But when Michelle can''t decide whether to draw Teddy or Denise, they quit being friends with her.', 7, 21, '5 Apr. 1994'),
(10207, 'tt0584092', '140', 'A Date with Fate', 'MV5BMTU1Nzk4MDA3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzk2Njg3MjE@', 'Danny''s date and D.J.''s date meet and become attracted to each other. Rebecca''s sons, Nicky and Alexander, learn a Mother''s Day song.', 7, 22, '3 May 1994'),
(10208, 'tt0584242', '140', 'Too Little Richard Too Late', 'MV5BMTQ4MzIyNzM4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjQ2Njg3MjE@', 'To help try and save the art program at Michelle''s school, Joey runs for president of the PTA. Little Richard guest stars as Denise''s uncle and performs at Joey''s pre-election rally.', 7, 23, '10 May 1994'),
(10209, 'tt0584094', '140', 'A House Divided', 'MV5BNzM3MjU2NDc5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA3Njg3MjE@', 'A rich man who used to live in the Tanner house makes Danny a handsome offer to buy it back. The rest of the family''s excited about moving on to new and bigger places, but Michelle tries to stop the sale so the family won''t split up.', 7, 24, '17 May 1994'),
(10210, 'tt0584118', '140', 'Comet''s Excellent Adventure', 'MV5BODU5MTY3MjMwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA3Njg3MjE@', 'Comet, the dog, runs away. The Rippers no longer want Jesse in their band. D.J. ends a relationship with a rich boyfriend.', 8, 1, '27 Sep. 1994'),
(10211, 'tt0584110', '140', 'Breaking Away', 'MV5BNTA0OTgzNDQ2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ3Njg3MjE@', 'Rebecca and Jesse are apprehensive about their twin boys attending preschool. Stephanie becomes rebellious due to a friend''s influence.', 8, 2, '4 Oct. 1994'),
(10212, 'tt0584172', '140', 'Making Out Is Hard to Do', 'MV5BMjM2OTExMzQ4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDY1Njg3MjE@', 'When invited to Gia''s place for a party, Stephanie arrives, but the other kids have more advanced games in mind for the evening.', 8, 3, '11 Oct. 1994'),
(10213, 'tt0584152', '140', 'I''ve Got a Secret', 'MV5BMTg3MTY0MjIwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTk3Njg3MjE@', 'Danny causes problems for Michelle when she joins a secret club. D.J. becomes jealous when Kimmy dates her former boyfriend. Jesse and Rebecca agree to divulge the names of their past loves.', 8, 4, '18 Oct. 1994'),
(10214, 'tt0584241', '140', 'To Joey, with Love', 'MV5BMTg5ODU0NTcwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjM2Njg3MjE@', 'Joey takes a job as a substitute teacher--in Michelle''s classroom. PTA president, Mrs. Carruthers (guest star MARCIA WALLACE) becomes Joey''s not-so-secret admirer. Danny auditions to play bass guitar for Jesse.', 8, 5, '25 Oct. 1994'),
(10215, 'tt0776078', '140', 'You Pet It, You Bought It', 'MV5BMTQ0MzQzNzAxMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQxMDg3MjE@', 'Michelle buys a donkey from the petting zoo.', 8, 6, '1 Nov. 1994'),
(10216, 'tt0584183', '140', 'On the Road Again', 'MV5BMjM3MDI1MjM1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY1Njg3MjE@', 'When Danny finds out that D.J. is secretly dating the guitarist in Jesse''s new band, Danny forbids her to continue.', 8, 7, '8 Nov. 1994'),
(10217, 'tt0584116', '140', 'Claire and Present Danger', 'MV5BMjA0MTUyMzgyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTI3Njg3MjE@', 'Danny asks the mother of Stephanie''s friend Gia out on a date--causing Michelle to rebel. Joey is surprised when the French woman he asked out on a date arrives with her husband. Jesse is nervous about his first appearance with his new band.', 8, 8, '22 Nov. 1994'),
(10218, 'tt0584205', '140', 'Stephanie''s Wild Ride', 'MV5BMTY1NTI5NjYxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDI3MzE1NTE@', 'Stephanie and Gia meet a couple of older guys at the mall, who invite the girls to go for a spin. When the guys turn out to be totally reckless drivers, Stephanie is torn between her better judgment, and her desire to let loose and have fun. Meanwhile, th', 8, 9, '29 Nov. 1994'),
(10219, 'tt0584247', '140', 'Under the Influence', 'MV5BNDE1NTgwMDgyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY2Njg3MjE@', 'D.J.''s friendship with Kimmy is put to a severe test after D.J. forcibly removes a very drunk Kimmy from a college fraternity party.', 8, 10, '6 Dec. 1994'),
(10220, 'tt0584102', '140', 'Arrest Ye Merry Gentlemen', 'MV5BNTM1MTU5MjUwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE3Njg3MjE@', 'Michelle saves up to buy the perfect present for her father for Christmas. Later Becky buys the same present as a gag gift for Joey, and the whole family Laughs at it. Michelle forces Jesse to take her to return it on Christmas eve but the store clerk won', 8, 11, '13 Dec. 1994'),
(10221, 'tt0584123', '140', 'D.J.''s Choice', 'MV5BMjQ1MTYyMzg4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTQ3Njg3MjE@', 'Both Nelson and Viper compete to be D.J.''s boyfriend. Nelson hires FRANKIE VALLI (himself) to serenade her. Michelle leads the family on a crusade to clean up a vandalized playground.', 8, 12, '3 Jan. 1995'),
(10222, 'tt0584230', '140', 'The Producer', 'MV5BMjg4NzU2MTMwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI2Njg3MjE@', 'Danny feels humiliated and quits when Rebecca is promoted to producer of the show. (Original Broadcast: Season 8, Episode 13)', 8, 13, '10 Jan. 1995'),
(10223, 'tt0584207', '140', 'Super Bowl Fun Day', 'MV5BMjQ4MTkxMzc2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTg1Njg3MjE@', 'Joey comes home from a two-week comedy tour to watch the Super Bowl Game, forgetting that he and Jesse had volunteered to take Michelle''s science group to the museum that day. He takes them to the local bar so that he can watch the game and promises the k', 8, 14, '25 Jan. 1995'),
(10224, 'tt0774214', '140', 'My Left and Right Foot', 'MV5BNDcwMjMxMTgzNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkxOTc3MjE@', 'Michelle, frets about the size of her feet, after DJ and Kimmy were teasing her, at the shoe store.', 8, 15, '31 Jan. 1995'),
(10225, 'tt0584098', '140', 'Air Jesse', 'MV5BMzkzOTAzODY4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA3Njg3MjE@', 'When D.J and Kimmy plan a celebrity charity basketball game, D.J. recruits her family to play. Jesse is embarrassed to admit he can''t play basketball. Jesse is coached by a pro--KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR (himself). ADAM ABDUL-JABBAR appears with his dad.', 8, 16, '7 Feb. 1995'),
(10226, 'tt0584127', '140', 'Dateless in San Francisco', 'MV5BMTQyMjE1MTkzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjY3Njg3MjE@', 'Michelle gets a boyfriend for Valentine''s Day, while Joey gets a secret admirer. When Jesse helps Danny plan an elaborate date with Claire, Rebecca feels neglected.', 8, 17, '14 Feb. 1995'),
(10227, 'tt0584250', '140', 'We Got the Beat', 'MV5BNjczMTIzOTk2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDE2Njg3MjE@', 'Stephanie, her friends and Kimmy form their own band, and allow Jesse to be their manager. Jesse proves too demanding and too critical, so they drop him and attempt to make it on their own.', 8, 18, '21 Feb. 1995'),
(10228, 'tt0584210', '140', 'Taking the Plunge', 'MV5BMTc3MTcxMDM0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA2Njg3MjE@', 'It''s D.J. to the rescue when she learns that Kimmy plans to elope with her new boyfriend, hoping that marriage will solve all her problems. Joey gets an opportunity to meet the Queen of England.', 8, 19, '28 Feb. 1995'),
(10229, 'tt0584248', '140', 'Up on the Roof', 'MV5BNzY0OTMzOTcyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjU2Njg3MjE@', 'D.J. sets out to perform the ultimate senior prank in an attempt to top her Uncle Jesse. She got the idea to lift Principal Robolard''s car onto the school roof via a crane driven by Kimmy''s boyfriend. The prank took off without a hitch with just two small', 8, 20, '14 Mar. 1995'),
(10230, 'tt0584164', '140', 'Leap of Faith', 'MV5BMTY2MTQ4OTUzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTE3MzE1NTE@', 'Jesse tries to stop Rebecca from bungee jumping--but thinks it''s okay if he takes risks. Michelle cons her dad into letting her go to a rock concert. (Original Broadcast: Season 8, Episode 21)', 8, 21, '21 Mar. 1995'),
(10231, 'tt0584099', '140', 'All Stood Up', 'MV5BMjI2NDcwNjY4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjE3Njg3MjE@', 'Stephanie asks a boy to the dance and he does not show. Danny goes to talk to him and embarrasses Stephanie. Jesse has to relax but Kimmy and her distractions keep him from doing so.', 8, 22, '4 Apr. 1995'),
(10232, 'tt0584174', '140', 'Michelle Rides Again: Part 1', 'MV5BNjI3MTA3ODc0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzY1Njg3MjE@', 'While out horseback riding, Michelle''s horse runs into a tree, throwing her and causing her to hit her head.', 8, 23, '23 May 1995'),
(10233, 'tt0584175', '140', 'Michelle Rides Again: Part 2', 'MV5BMjM0MTc4Mzc2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDU1Njg3MjE@', 'The Tanner family helps Michelle try to regain her memory.', 8, 24, '23 May 1995'),
(10234, 'tt3464768', '141', 'Uno', 'MV5BOTgzMjM2MDg0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxNTYyNDE@', 'Jimmy tries an unconventional method for pursuing potential clients after inspiration strikes.', 1, 1, '8 Feb. 2015'),
(10235, 'tt3857028', '141', 'Mijo', 'MV5BNDIxOTMxNDgxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE0NjE0NDE@', 'Jimmy is taken hostage by the ruthless Tuco Salamanca, and desperately plans his escape.', 1, 2, '9 Feb. 2015'),
(10236, 'tt3858672', '141', 'Nacho', 'MV5BMTUxMjgxMjg0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTc4NzM3NjE@', 'Jimmy must prove that Nacho is innocent when he is wrongly suspected of kidnapping.', 1, 3, '16 Feb. 2015'),
(10237, 'tt3864892', '141', 'Hero', 'MV5BMTk0NjMzMzU3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzEyNTYyNDE@', 'Jimmy makes a bold move against Hamlin in an effort to attract potential clients.', 1, 4, '23 Feb. 2015'),
(10238, 'tt3876380', '141', 'Alpine Shepherd Boy', 'MV5BNDU2MjYxODk0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTcwNjU2NDE@', 'After a strange encounter with the police, Chuck ends up in the hospital. Jimmy meets up with a series of unruly clients.', 1, 5, '2 Mar. 2015'),
