(10864, 'tt0763046', '147', 'Best Friends Forever', 'MV5BODk3OTQ3NzgwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM0Mjk0MjE@', 'Can Cartman and Kenny stay as "Best Friends Forever", even when Kenny buys the last PSP in stock?', 9, 4, '30 Mar. 2005'),
(10865, 'tt0763051', '147', 'The Losing Edge', 'MV5BMjA5MjkxNzM2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI0Mjk0MjE@', 'The boys enlist Kyle''s cousin to help them lose in baseball so they won''t have to go to the finals. Meanwhile, Randy trains to fight other parents during Stan''s games.', 9, 5, '6 Apr. 2005'),
