(10867, 'tt0763047', '147', 'Erection Day', 'MV5BMjM2MDM1MTM1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ0Mjk0MjE@', 'Jimmy gets his first erection just days before the school talent show.', 9, 7, '20 Apr. 2005'),
(10868, 'tt0763053', '147', 'Two Days Before the Day After Tomorrow', 'MV5BMTY3NzcwNTkyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTkzMjk0MjE@', 'When a dam breaks and floods a nearby town, South Park residents assume it was caused by global warming and barricade themselves in the community center.', 9, 8, '19 Oct. 2005'),
(10869, 'tt0761291', '147', 'Marjorine', 'MV5BMjE4MjI2OTEwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTUxMDk0MjE@', 'Butters fake his own death and disguises himself as a girl so he can infiltrate a sleepover and steal a fortune telling device from the girls. Meanwhile, Butters'' father turns to the occult to bring back his son.', 9, 9, '26 Oct. 2005'),
(10870, 'tt0705925', '147', 'Follow That Egg', 'MV5BMjE2ODUwNTA2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzk5NTg0MjE@', 'Mr Garrison realises he still has feelings for Mr Slave. But Mr Slave has moved on and plans to marry his new boyfriend, Big Gay Al as soon as the Governor signs the same sex marriage bill.', 9, 10, '2 Nov. 2005'),
(10871, 'tt0761286', '147', 'Ginger Kids', 'MV5BNjk2OTA2MjgwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTQzNDE1NTE@', 'Cartman leads a vendetta against kids with red hair and freckles, until a prank makes him think he is one of them.', 9, 11, '9 Nov. 2005'),
(10872, 'tt0761294', '147', 'Trapped in the Closet', 'MV5BMTgxMTM3MDQzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQzNDE1NTE@', 'After Stan scores a remarkably high "Thetan Level" at a Scientology center, he is considered to be the reincarnation of Scientology founder L. Ron Hubbard. John Travolta, Tom Cruise and other Scientologists go to South Park to convince Stan to be their le', 9, 12, '16 Nov. 2005'),
(10873, 'tt0761285', '147', 'Free Willzyx', 'MV5BMTgwMzQ4MTUwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTExMDk0MjE@', 'When a prank convinces the boys that a whale in a local aquarium is an alien from the moon, they go to extreme measures to sent it home.', 9, 13, '30 Nov. 2005'),
(10874, 'tt0761283', '147', 'Bloody Mary', 'MV5BMjM3Nzk4NDI4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDIxMDk0MjE@', 'Randy is forced to go to AA meetings, where he becomes convinced that he has a disease. Desperate, he and Stan go on a pilgrimage to a statue of the virgin Mary that is miraculously bleeding from its ass.', 9, 14, '7 Dec. 2005'),
(10875, 'tt0780944', '147', 'The Return of Chef', 'MV5BMTQwOTM1NDU5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODYyMDk0MjE@', 'Chef returns to town after joining a group called The Super Adventure Club. However, when he begins to express an interest in molesting children, the boys suspect that the club has brainwashed him.', 10, 1, '22 Mar. 2006'),
(10876, 'tt0783418', '147', 'Smug Alert!', 'MV5BMTgxMDc1OTgyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTYyNzg0MjE@', 'Stan convinces everyone in South Park to drive Hybrid cars after Kyle moves to San Francisco. However, soon a dangerous cloud of "smug" forms over South Park.', 10, 2, '29 Mar. 2006'),
(10877, 'tt0786244', '147', 'Cartoon Wars: Part 1', 'MV5BMjE4NjE3MTQyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY0NDE1NTE@', 'Cartman begins a one-man crusade to get "Family Guy" taken off the air after it shows an image of Mohammed. But his real motive is not that it''s offensive to Muslims--it''s because the show''s not funny.', 10, 3, '5 Apr. 2006'),
(10878, 'tt0789661', '147', 'Cartoon Wars: Part 2', 'MV5BMTQ1ODc1MDg5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY0NDE1NTE@', 'Cartman finds an unlikely ally in his quest to get "Family Guy" off the air: Bart Simpson. He also discovers Fox''s surprising secret about the show''s writers.', 10, 4, '12 Apr. 2006'),
(10879, 'tt0793257', '147', 'A Million Little Fibers', 'MV5BMTQxODA0ODU0Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODAxMzk0MjE@', 'Towelie''s autobiography, "A Million Little Fibers", becomes Oprah Winfrey''s official Book of the Month selection and a bestseller... but for how long?', 10, 5, '19 Apr. 2006'),
(10880, 'tt0795284', '147', 'ManBearPig', 'MV5BMTkzMTcyNDY2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjYzMTk0MjE@', 'A lonely and attention-desperate Al Gore comes to South Park Elementary to explain the dangers of the biggest threat to the planet: Manbearpig. Although the kids believe Gore uses Manbearpig as a way of gaining attention, they decide to help him capture t', 10, 6, '26 Apr. 2006'),
(10881, 'tt0799356', '147', 'Tsst', 'MV5BMjM3NTIwMTQ4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODU0ODg0MjE@', 'Eric''s mom turns to a "dog whisperer" as a last resort to turn him to a good little boy. The whisperer is successful in making Eric calm and submissive, but he may have also turned him into a repressed killer.', 10, 7, '3 May 2006'),
(10882, 'tt0850173', '147', 'Make Love, Not Warcraft', 'MV5BMjI1NzY0MTIwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTM3NDE1NTE@', 'The kids work around the clock to improve their character skills in "World of Warcraft" so that they can beat a fellow gamer who keeps violating the rules and killing everyone else''s characters.', 10, 8, '4 Oct. 2006'),
(10883, 'tt0871765', '147', 'Mystery of the Urinal Deuce', 'MV5BMTUxMzYxNzkyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzAwMjk0MjE@', 'Kyle sets out to prove that 9/11 wasn''t a government conspiracy, and actually uncovers a government conspiracy to create a conspiracy.', 10, 9, '11 Oct. 2006'),
(10884, 'tt0882614', '147', 'Miss Teacher Bangs a Boy', 'MV5BMTgzNjE5ODU2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjkxMDk0MjE@', 'Kyle discovers that his brother Ike is having a sexual relationship with his kindergarten teacher. The police are reluctant to help, so Kyle is forced to turn to the new school hall monitor for help: Eric "Dawg" Cartman.', 10, 10, '18 Oct. 2006'),
(10885, 'tt0887071', '147', 'Hell on Earth 2006', 'MV5BMTY0MTAwNzYxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzgxNjk0NTE@', 'Satan returns to Earth to throw a huge members-only Holloween party in Los Angeles, and the boys keep summoning the ghost of Biggie Smalls--which means that he''s going to miss the party.', 10, 11, '25 Oct. 2006'),
(10886, 'tt0890648', '147', 'Go God Go', 'MV5BMjEwODQ2MDEzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk2Mjg0MjE@', 'Cartman tries to cryogenically freeze himself so that he doesn''t have to wait for the new Nintendo machine, and Ms. Garrison falls for the new Evolution teacher and becomes an Atheist.', 10, 12, '1 Nov. 2006'),
