(10888, 'tt0897215', '147', 'Stanley''s Cup', 'MV5BMzQ3MjI2ODMyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTg4NTg0MjE@', 'Stan Marsh has hit rock bottom. He''s got no job, no bicycle and his only way out of a bad situation, is to coach the local pee wee hockey team. Once a hotshot pee wee hockey player himself, Stan Marsh has tried to put those days behind him. But he''s still', 10, 14, '15 Nov. 2006'),
(10889, 'tt0940288', '147', 'With Apologies to Jesse Jackson', 'MV5BMjA5MTg5ODM0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ5NTg0MjE@', 'Stan becomes a social outcast after his father Randy says "the N-Word" on national television, but Michael Richards and Mark Furhman come to Randy''s rescue.', 11, 1, '7 Mar. 2007'),
(10890, 'tt0948344', '147', 'Cartman Sucks', 'MV5BMTQzMzE4Njg1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzk5NDE1NTE@', 'Cartman takes a photo with Butters''s penis in his mouth to prove Butters is gay. He later finds out what the picture really means and freaks out when the photo disappears. Meanwhile, Butters to has to go to a special camp to calm his urges.', 11, 2, '14 Mar. 2007'),
(10891, 'tt0983724', '147', 'Lice Capades', 'MV5BMjA4NzE4MTcxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzYyMzg0MjE@', 'A lice outbreak hits Ms. Garrison''s class, and at least one parasite is determined to survive after his lice civilization is destroyed.', 11, 3, '21 Mar. 2007'),
(10892, 'tt0983725', '147', 'The Snuke', 'MV5BNjI5OTgwMjA0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTgzMzg0MjE@', 'While trying to find a way to persecute the new Arab kid in his class, Cartman accidentally uncovers an unrelated plot to assassinate Hillary Clinton at a South Park political rally.', 11, 4, '28 Mar. 2007'),
(10893, 'tt0983726', '147', 'Fantastic Easter Special', 'MV5BMzc0NDQxNjcwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTgyMzg0MjE@', 'In a parody of "The daVinci Code," Stan discovers the real reason behind Easter, decorating eggs, and the Easter Bunny.', 11, 5, '4 Apr. 2007'),
(10894, 'tt0983727', '147', 'D-Yikes!', 'MV5BMTQzOTQ1NjYzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDMyMzg0MjE@', 'Ms. Garrison''s latest date goes so badly that she assigns the class the book report over the weekend, but the boys hire immigrant labor to write it. Meanwhile, Ms. Garrison becomes a lesbian and saves the women''s bar from a Persian takeover.', 11, 6, '11 Apr. 2007'),
(10895, 'tt0995581', '147', 'Night of the Living Homeless', 'MV5BMTk2NjAyNzE0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjA4Mjk0MjE@', 'One day after Kyle gives $20 to a homeless person, South Park becomes overrun with panhandlers.', 11, 7, '18 Apr. 2007'),
