(10897, 'tt0995583', '147', 'More Crap', 'MV5BMjI2NzEyODM3NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjY3Mjk0MjE@', 'Randy Marsh sets the world record for the biggest bowel movement, until Bono comes along and challenges it.', 11, 9, '10 Oct. 2007'),
(10898, 'tt0995577', '147', 'Imaginationland', 'MV5BMTc0NDE1ODcxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTA4Mjk0MjE@', 'Cartman takes Kyle to court because he refuses to follow through with his promise to suck Cartman''s balls if they see a Leprechaun. Meanwhile, Muslim extremists attack "Imaginationland," and the government plans a counter-attack.', 11, 10, '17 Oct. 2007'),
(10899, 'tt0995578', '147', 'Imaginationland: Episode II', 'MV5BNzA0NDU4ODI1Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk3Mjk0MjE@', 'With the help of Stan, Kyle, and Kurt Russell, the military is able to access the portal to Imaginationland. Meanwhile, Cartman is determined to make sure that Kyle follows through with his court-mandated sentence.', 11, 11, '24 Oct. 2007'),
(10900, 'tt0995579', '147', 'Imaginationland: Episode III', 'MV5BMTk0ODI2MzY5NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzk3Mjk0MjE@', 'All hope appears to be lost for Imaginationland, until it is discovered that Butters has the power to lead them to victory. And will Cartman ever get Kyle to suck his balls?', 11, 12, '31 Oct. 2007'),
(10901, 'tt0995580', '147', 'Guitar Queer-o', 'MV5BOTE3Njg4MTE0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk3Mjk0MjE@', 'Stan and Kyle become local celebrities after they score 100,000 points on the video game "Guitar Hero." A talent agent signs them to a contract, which ends up ruining their friendship.', 11, 13, '7 Nov. 2007'),
(10902, 'tt1137316', '147', 'The List', 'MV5BMjQwNjA1MjI1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE3MDk0MjE@', 'The girls in the fourth grade class have made a secret list that rates every boy''s looks from cutest to ugliest. When the boys steal the list, they are completely unprepared to deal with the results.', 11, 14, '14 Nov. 2007'),
(10903, 'tt1198003', '147', 'Tonsil Trouble', 'MV5BOTkxNDY4NjA4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjI2NTE1NTE@', 'After Cartman and Kyle are infected with the AIDS virus, they turn to Magic Johnson for assistance in finding a cure.', 12, 1, '12 Mar. 2008'),
(10904, 'tt1205578', '147', 'Britney''s New Look', 'MV5BNzQ5NzMxNjI5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk4MTk0MjE@', 'Distraught over the media''s nonstop coverage of her, Britney Spears attempts to commit suicide, but survives despite blowing the top half of her head off. Disgusted by this treatment of her, the boys attempt to help, only to learn the secret behind the me', 12, 2, '19 Mar. 2008'),
(10905, 'tt1207526', '147', 'Major Boobage', 'MV5BMTU0NjYzMzg1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTEyMzk0MjE@', 'South Park declares cats illegal after kids start getting high on cat urine. Cartman starts hiding neighborhood cats in his attic to protect them, and Kenny becomes an addict and starts having M&eacute;tal hurlant (1981) hallucinations.', 12, 3, '26 Mar. 2008'),
(10906, 'tt1211261', '147', 'Canada on Strike', 'MV5BODQwODM2Nzc0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQzMjg0MjE@', 'Canada goes on strike and demands more money, but nobody takes the strike seriously. However, the boys try to make money for Canada by turning Butters into an Internet video star.', 12, 4, '2 Apr. 2008'),
(10907, 'tt1213538', '147', 'Eek, a Penis!', 'MV5BNTQ3MzE0MTgxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTY2NDg0MjE@', 'Cartman is commended for his excellent substitute teaching, so he his brought to the inner city to help the high schoolers. Meanwhile, Ms. Garrison wants to be Mr. Garrison again.', 12, 5, '9 Apr. 2008'),
(10908, 'tt1218415', '147', 'Over Logging', 'MV5BMjU4NDczOTU0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkzODg0MjE@', 'A prolonged Internet service outage hits South Park and most of the rest of the country, and Randy moves the Marsh family to California hoping to find a connection (and Internet porn for himself).', 12, 6, '16 Apr. 2008'),
(10909, 'tt1220462', '147', 'Super Fun Time', 'MV5BNzI2MjQ1MzExNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTI3NTE1NTE@', 'A class field trip to a frontier park turns into a hostage situation when a group of robbers use the park to evade the police, but the park employees won''t help resolve the situation because they won''t get out of character.', 12, 7, '23 Apr. 2008'),
(10910, 'tt1221771', '147', 'The China Probrem', 'MV5BMjA3OTcyOTUyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzM3MDk0MjE@', 'Cartman and Butters go to P.F. Chang''s to try to uncover the Chinese conspiracy to take over the U.S.. Stan and Kyle accuse Steven Spielberg and George Lucas of raping Indiana Jones', 12, 8, '8 Oct. 2008'),
(10911, 'tt1307777', '147', 'Breast Cancer Show Ever', 'MV5BMjIxMzU2MDY3NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk0MDk0MjE@', 'Cartman makes fun of Wendy after she delivers a report on breast cancer. She challenges him to a fight, but he keeps finding ways to get out of it. But he also won''t stop making fun of her.', 12, 9, '15 Oct. 2008'),
(10912, 'tt1312012', '147', 'Pandemic', 'MV5BMTQyMjg1NTAwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg5Mzk0MjE@', 'With Craig''s help, the boys start up a Peruvian pan flute band to make money. However, they are detained by Homeland Security and sent to Peru to end the "Pandemic." In the pan flute bands'' absence, giant guinea pigs invade South Park.', 12, 10, '22 Oct. 2008'),
(10913, 'tt1312846', '147', 'Pandemic 2: The Startling', 'MV5BMjA4MjM4ODc1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk4Mjk0MjE@', 'Craig and the boys are stranded in the Andes Mountains while giant guinea pigs wreak havoc all over the planet. Craig is the only person who can end the terror, but he doesn''t care and won''t do anything about it.', 12, 11, '29 Oct. 2008'),
(10914, 'tt1312843', '147', 'About Last Night...', 'MV5BNjE2NjA4MDAxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM5Mjk0MjE@', 'While the rest of the nation is distracted by the results of the presidential election, Barack Obama and John McCain set out to complete their true combined objective: a daring "Ocean''s Eleven" style jewel heist.', 12, 12, '5 Nov. 2008'),
(10915, 'tt1312844', '147', 'Elementary School Musical', 'MV5BOTk4NjUwNDA4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjI5Mjk0MjE@', 'The boys try to resist the "High School Musical" fad when it hits South Park Elementary, while also trying to convince the school''s top singer that he should follow his dream and try out for the basketball team.', 12, 13, '12 Nov. 2008'),
(10916, 'tt1312845', '147', 'The Ungroundable', 'MV5BMTUzNzY5MjY0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI5Mjk0MjE@', 'Butters starts hanging out with the Vampire kids, who are angering the Goth kids at South Park Elementary because everybody is confusing the Vampire kids with them.', 12, 14, '19 Nov. 2008'),
(10917, 'tt1390286', '147', 'The Ring', 'MV5BMTcwNTA1ODIxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTk2OTg1Mg@@', 'The boys discover that the Jonas Brothers'' purity ring campaign is just part of Disney''s plot to get away with marketing sex to pre-teen girls.', 13, 1, '11 Mar. 2009'),
(10918, 'tt1395555', '147', 'The Coon', 'MV5BNDg3MjEzMDc2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTgxMzg0MjE@', 'Cartman tries to become a superhero, only to have another fourth grader steal his thunder by becoming one too and becoming more popular.', 13, 2, '18 Mar. 2009'),
(10919, 'tt1397941', '147', 'Margaritaville', 'MV5BMTI0NDY4NjAxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzk2OTg1Mg@@', 'In a parody of the final weeks of Christ''s life, South Park goes into hysterics over the failing economy, but Kyle begins preaching that there is no reason for fear. Meanwhile, Stan unsuccessfully tries to return his dad''s margarita machine.', 13, 3, '25 Mar. 2009');
