(11082, 'tt2261314', '150', 'The Milkmaid''s Lot', 'MV5BODE3Mjk0OTM2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTgyNzQ3OA@@', 'Nucky is still feeling the effects of the bomb concussion as Rothstein and other allies withdraw their support while Margaret and Owen come to an understanding.', 3, 10, '11 Nov. 2012'),
