(11085, 'tt2261328', '150', 'Margate Sands', 'MV5BMTY5MDE1OTkxMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTg1Nzk3OA@@', 'After promising Rothstein Mellon''s distillery, Masseria is persuaded to withdraw his support for Gyp, and Margaret finds an abortionist in Brooklyn.', 3, 13, '2 Dec. 2012'),
