(12011, 'tt0997135', '164', 'Truth and Justice', 'MV5BMjAwMDQzMzc5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzg1MDcyNzE@', 'Cardinal Campeggio''s long awaited papal legation has arrived at court to decide with colleague-cardinal Thomas Wolsey on the royal request for divorce, claiming Catherine''s first marriage to Henry''s late elder brother nullified his. When Campeggio learns ', 1, 8, '20 May 2007'),
(12012, 'tt0997136', '164', 'Look to God First', 'MV5BMTk3NDY2MzQ4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQ5OTUzNzE@', 'The legatine court''s divorce trial continues in the Queen''s absence, hearing testimony suggesting prince Arthur carnally consummated his marriage to Catherine: embarrassing for the court, amusing for the populace. Catherine''s council, bishop Fisher, dares', 1, 9, '3 Jun. 2007'),
(12013, 'tt0997129', '164', 'The Death of Wolsey', 'MV5BMjE5NjczOTI4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTc1MDcyNzE@', 'Now cardinal Wolsey lives in misery as penniless archbishop of and in York, barred from court, hoping in vain Ann Boleyn who broke his hold on the king will reward his efforts as she once wrote, honors and offices are mainly distributed to the Boleyn clan', 1, 10, '10 Jun. 2007'),
(12014, 'tt1014043', '164', 'Everything Is Beautiful', 'MV5BMTEzMjM1MDU3NTReQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDkyNzA3Mjcx', 'As he seeks the annulment of his marriage to Katherine of Aragon, King Henry VIII appoints himself the head of the Church of England. And Anne Boleyn insists that Henry remove Queen Katherine from the picture -- and Court.', 2, 1, '30 Mar. 2008'),
(12015, 'tt1014045', '164', 'Tears of Blood', 'MV5BMTQ4NTc0ODgyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI1NzEzNzE@', 'The Archbishop''s capitulation to Henry results in Thomas More''s resignation and a triumphal trip by Henry to France to show off his new queen to Francis.', 2, 2, '6 Apr. 2008'),
(12016, 'tt1014046', '164', 'Checkmate', 'MV5BMTQ0OTQ5ODg1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjM3MDcyNzE@', 'After Henry breaks all ties with the church and marries Anne, the Pope threatens him with excommunication and authorizes Anne''s assassination.', 2, 3, '13 Apr. 2008'),
(12017, 'tt1014047', '164', 'The Act of Succession', 'MV5BMjQzNDc5MDM1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDM3MDcyNzE@', 'After princess Elisabeth''s baptism, Henry orders Thomas Cromwell to draw up a bill of succession favoring his and Ann''s offspring, to be accepted by an oath from all subjects. The affront to the imperialist party is maximized by making princess Mary a low', 2, 4, '20 Apr. 2008'),
(12018, 'tt1014048', '164', 'His Majesty''s Pleasure', 'MV5BMjA0Nzc3NDQ4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ3MDcyNzE@', 'Fisher and More continue to resist the coercion to take the oath and pay with their lives as Henry''s ardor toward Anne subsides after her miscarriage.', 2, 5, '27 Apr. 2008'),
(12019, 'tt1014049', '164', 'The Definition of Love', 'MV5BMjI1NTY2NzAzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODM3MDcyNzE@', 'When King Francis refuses to approve an engagement involving the baby but proposes one between Mary and the Dauphin, Henry begins to turn against Anne.', 2, 6, '4 May 2008'),
(12020, 'tt1014050', '164', 'Matters of State', 'MV5BMTg5NjA2MzMxMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ3MDcyNzE@', 'Henry warns Anne to stay out of state affairs, but her paranoiac fear of Catherine is only alleviated with her death and Anne''s new pregnancy.', 2, 7, '11 May 2008'),
(12021, 'tt1014051', '164', 'Lady in Waiting', 'MV5BMjExMzk0OTY0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjQ3MDcyNzE@', 'The Pope excommunicates Henry, who recovers after a near-fatal jousting accident and begins a relationship with Jane Seymour.', 2, 8, '18 May 2008'),
(12022, 'tt1014052', '164', 'The Act of Treason', 'MV5BMjA2ODEwNzAyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ3MDcyNzE@', 'As Jane Seymour''s fortunes rise, Anne''s fall. Several of those close to her including her brother are tortured into confessing treason and beheaded.', 2, 9, '25 May 2008'),
(12023, 'tt1014044', '164', 'Destiny and Fortune', 'MV5BMTc2MDg4MTE2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM3MDcyNzE@', 'Anne goes to her death continuing to pronounce her innocence and that of the accused men.', 2, 10, '1 Jun. 2008'),
(12024, 'tt1384333', '164', 'Civil Unrest', 'MV5BOTkyMDA2NzI0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjgzMTcyNzE@', 'Henry''s new wife Jane urges him to reconcile with his daughter Mary while Robert Aske leads a pilgrimage of thousands against Cromwell''s monastic reforms.', 3, 1, '5 Apr. 2009'),
(12025, 'tt1390788', '164', 'The Northern Uprising', 'MV5BMTUyMzAzMzcwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTczMTcyNzE@', 'The Duke of Suffolk is unable to defeat the rebellion militarily, so he resorts to lies and subterfuges.', 3, 2, '12 Apr. 2009'),
(12026, 'tt1401057', '164', 'Dissension and Punishment', 'MV5BODM0NjgxMDE5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI1MDYzNzE@', 'Henry feigns reconciliation with Aske but ultimately has the leaders of the rebellion arrested; later he becomes ecstatic over Jane''s pregnancy.', 3, 3, '19 Apr. 2009'),
(12027, 'tt1401058', '164', 'The Death of a Queen', 'MV5BMTkxMzc0MzkzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk0ODY0NzE@', 'Forced to recant, Aske is hanged in Yorkshire, Cromwell coerces Brandon to execute more rebels as examples, and Jane suffers complications in childbirth.', 3, 4, '26 Apr. 2009'),
