(12029, 'tt1401060', '164', 'Search for a New Queen', 'MV5BMTYzODU5MzEyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDUzMTcyNzE@', 'frustrated in his efforts to assassinate Cardinal Pole, Henry has his relatives executed while Cromwell supports a marriage to Anne of Cleves.', 3, 6, '10 May 2009'),
(12030, 'tt1401061', '164', 'Protestant Anne of Cleves', 'MV5BMjA4OTc5ODQ2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI1MDYzNzE@', 'Henry settles on Anne Of Cleves as his fourth wife but is disappointed with her attractiveness and blames Cromwell for his unhappy situation.', 3, 7, '17 May 2009'),
(12031, 'tt1401062', '164', 'The Undoing of Cromwell', 'MV5BMTA3NDQwNzMwNjZeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDI1MzE3Mjcx', 'As Henry seeks to have his marriage to Anne of Cleves annulled and Cromwell removed, Bryan pimps teenage Catherine Howard as Henry''s new mistress.', 3, 8, '24 May 2009'),
(12032, 'tt1619578', '164', 'Moment of Nostalgia', 'MV5BMjAwNTM1OTU5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjE3MTcyNzE@', 'Henry is proud of Catherine, his beautiful, vivacious seventeen year old wife, who buys silence from an old friend by making her a member of the court.', 4, 1, '11 Apr. 2010'),
(12033, 'tt1621746', '164', 'Sister', 'MV5BMjIzNDUwMTU5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzcwMTYzNzE@', 'Joan Bulmer confides the Queen''s sexual history to Lady Rochford who tells it to Culpepper and arranges for him to have a liaison with the neglected Catherine.', 4, 2, '18 Apr. 2010'),
(12034, 'tt1647295', '164', 'Something for You', 'MV5BMTQ1NDEzNTk2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA4MTcyNzE@', 'While Henry prepares for a politically important trip to meet the defeated Northern rebels, Queen Catherine carries on her passionate affair with Culpepper.', 4, 3, '25 Apr. 2010'),
(12035, 'tt1651851', '164', 'Natural Ally', 'MV5BMjIxNDY2OTc0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDgzNjE0NzE@', 'Catherine''s buys the silence of an indiscreet former lover with a position in her chamber as her affair with Culpepper becomes more tempestuous.', 4, 4, '2 May 2010'),
(12036, 'tt1653119', '164', 'Bottom of the Pot', 'MV5BMTQ5NDM0MDI0MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk3MTcyNzE@', 'After receiving a letter from an anonymous source the King decides to investigate the accusation that two other men knew Catherine ''carnally'' while she was under the service of the Dowager Duchess, and he confines his Queen to her apartments with only Lad', 4, 5, '9 May 2010'),
(12037, 'tt1652941', '164', 'You Have My Permission', 'MV5BMTc2NjQ3NDEyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzk3MTcyNzE@', 'Henry allows Bishop Gardner a free rein in rooting out heretics and sets his eyes on the soon-to-be-widowed Catherine Parr.', 4, 6, '16 May 2010'),
(12038, 'tt1629166', '164', 'Sixth and the Final Wife', 'MV5BMTQ5Nzk2NzgxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc2MTcyNzE@', 'After leaving wife Catherine as regent, a bellicose Henry invades France and lays siege to Boulogne in an attempt to regain his French provinces.', 4, 7, '23 May 2010'),
(12039, 'tt1661000', '164', 'As It Should Be', 'MV5BMTgzOTc5MjM3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzU3MTcyNzE@', 'Although Henry does take Boulogne, his troops are decimated by dysentery while back in England the Queen arranges to give Edward a tutor with Lutheran beliefs.', 4, 8, '6 Jun. 2010'),
(12040, 'tt1672555', '164', 'Secrets of the Heart', 'MV5BMjI0Mjg2OTk5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDM5MTcyNzE@', 'Surrey plots treason after being relieved of command, and as Bishop Gardiner''s inquisition proceeds, it comes closer and closer to the Queen.', 4, 9, '13 Jun. 2010'),
(12041, 'tt1672554', '164', 'Death of a Monarchy', 'MV5BNjExMzYxNDc1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk5NDIyMjE@', 'As Henry''s health deteriorates, he grows introspective as various factions in the court try to position themselves for the seemingly inevitable succession.', 4, 10, '20 Jun. 2010'),
(12042, 'tt3380658', '165', 'Night Zero', 'MV5BMjMwOTk4NjMwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTI4MzY4MTE@', 'When a commercial airliner lands and stands silent, CDC agent Ephraim Goodweather investigates the plane to find that the passengers are infected by a vile plague.', 1, 1, '13 Jul. 2014'),
(12043, 'tt3480884', '165', 'The Box', 'MV5BMTc1NTczOTQ3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk1OTMyMjE@', 'The four survivors begin manifesting strange symptoms, but Eph and Nora''s attempt to quarantine them is thwarted as the disinformation campaign begins. Meanwhile, in jail, Setrakian receives a surprise visit from an old - a very old - acquaintance.', 1, 2, '20 Jul. 2014'),
(12044, 'tt3428146', '165', 'Gone Smooth', 'MV5BMjM0MzA5MDUyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI3OTIzMjE@', 'Eph and Nora fight to save Captain Redfern''s life before coming face-to-face with the horrifying effects of the virus. A spike in rat attacks signals Fet that something inexplicable is happening deep below the city. Released from jail, Setrakian begins hi', 1, 3, '27 Jul. 2014'),
(12045, 'tt3410216', '165', 'It''s Not for Everyone', 'MV5BNjg1OTQ0NzgyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDI3OTIzMjE@', 'A secret autopsy demonstrates the bizarre progression of the mystery virus, prompting Jim to make a startling confession. Eph and Nora race to find the father of the youngest victim of the plane tragedy, but someone unexpected beats them to it. Ansel, in ', 1, 4, '3 Aug. 2014'),
(12046, 'tt3475844', '165', 'Runaways', 'MV5BMTgyODE2OTMwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDA1NDc5MjE@', 'With Nora gone, Eph reluctantly joins Setrakian''s quest in hopes of gathering enough evidence to warrant a citywide quarantine. Fet encounters the unexpected inside the subway tunnels, and a medical emergency threatens Palmer''s master plan.', 1, 5, '10 Aug. 2014'),
(12047, 'tt3613468', '165', 'Occultation', 'MV5BOTI0OTUzMTk4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzM4NDc5MjE@', 'After warning Kelly to leave the city with Zack ahead of the spreading plague, Eph is arrested by the FBI. Eichhorst has one final job for Gus, while Setrakian realizes that the coming eclipse is the tipping point for virus infection and the beginning of ', 1, 6, '17 Aug. 2014'),
(12048, 'tt3515200', '165', 'For Services Rendered', 'MV5BMTQ5NzUyOTMwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTgxNDk0MjE@', 'Setrakian, Eph, and Nora formulate a plan to track down the Master using Jim as bait. Eichhorst and Setrakian''s pasts are revealed. At the Luss home, Neeva struggles to protect the children while encountering a mysterious stranger whose help she may not w', 1, 7, '24 Aug. 2014'),
(12049, 'tt3646160', '165', 'Creatures of the Night', 'MV5BMTc2ODczNDUwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzk1NDc1MjE@', 'After discovering the potency of ultraviolet light against the strigoi, Setrakian gains a new and unlikely disciple. A quick trip to a Brooklyn convenience store turns into a deadly all-night siege.', 1, 8, '31 Aug. 2014'),
(12050, 'tt3515202', '165', 'The Disappeared', 'MV5BMTk5MzAxMTMzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTM0ODE2MjE@', 'Eph races to safeguard his family, only to learn that Kelly is missing. Dutch reveals her role in Palmer''s plan, and Gus is forced to make a difficult decision about Felix.', 1, 9, '7 Sep. 2014'),
