(12052, 'tt3630746', '165', 'The Third Rail', 'MV5BMTYwMTg2NzM4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQyOTM3MjE@', 'Setrakian leads Eph, Fet and Nora in the hunt for the Master''s lair. Left behind at the pawnshop with Mariela, Zack risks his safety for Mariela''s sake.', 1, 11, '21 Sep. 2014'),
(12053, 'tt3675166', '165', 'Last Rites', 'MV5BMTY1ODAzNzgyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjIwMjA4MjE@', 'Dutch returns with a plan to broadcast Eph''s warning about the vampiric plague. However, they face a new threat when Eichhorst launches his own attack against the pawn shop. Palmer receives a special visitor, and Gus gears up for the on-coming fight but d', 1, 12, '28 Sep. 2014'),
