(12055, 'tt3969926', '165', 'BK, NY', 'MV5BMjMxODA1NTkxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDM2MzcwNjE@', 'Eph and Nora work on a weapon to kill the strigoi, but Setrakian puts the group at risk by searching for an ancient text, while the Master introduces a new breed of creature and taps Kelly to control it.', 2, 1, '12 Jul. 2015'),
(12056, 'tt4174890', '165', 'By Any Means', 'MV5BMjM5ODA0MjQzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTM5ODIzNjE@', 'Vet and Dutch grow closer on a mission to make sure neighbourhood buildings are clear. Meanwhile, Eph and Nora perform experiments on their new patients; and Kelly begins her search for Zack.', 2, 2, '19 Jul. 2015'),
(12057, 'tt4229936', '165', 'Fort Defiance', 'MV5BMjI4OTk5MjY2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTc0MTA3NjE@', 'Gus and Vaun wage an attack on Palmer as Eph struggles to connect with Zack. Councilwoman Justine Faraldo vows to bring her extermination policies to the other boroughs.', 2, 3, '26 Jul. 2015'),
(12058, 'tt4247342', '165', 'The Silver Angel', 'MV5BNjc5ODg1MDA1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDM1NjU0NjE@', 'Eph and Nora finally see their lethal virus in action; Fet takes the security of Red Hook into his own hands; Dutch and Setrakian set off for Staten Island to question Fitzwilliam.', 2, 4, '2 Aug. 2015'),
(12059, 'tt4247344', '165', 'Quick and Painless', 'MV5BMjQyMDk1MjA0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODk3NjE1NjE@', 'Eph alters his appearance so he can leave the city, which makes Nora a reluctant parent for Zack. Meanwhile, Dutch and Nora negotiate with Justine to get Fet out of jail.', 2, 5, '9 Aug. 2015'),
