(12063, 'tt4247350', '165', 'The Battle for Red Hook', 'MV5BMTg1NDc2MzA0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc5MDk3NjE@', 'Justine takes drastic measures to counter a surprise invasion. Nora and Fet perform a useful mission while Eph and Setrakian face off against an old foe.', 2, 9, '6 Sep. 2015'),
