(12065, 'tt4247356', '165', 'Dead End', 'MV5BMTUyMDc2MTgwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA0MjU4NjE@', 'Gus helps the Guptas get across the border; Fet, Nora and Eph look all over the city for Dutch, who''s in a life-or-death struggle with Eichhorst; Setrakian meets a familiar face while searching for the Occido Lumen.', 2, 11, '20 Sep. 2015'),
(12066, 'tt4247358', '165', 'Fallen Light', 'MV5BOTQzMjg4NTU0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDM3MDI5NjE@', 'The Lumen''s auction starts in 24hrs. Setrakian seeks the Ancients backing. Gus seeks allies from his past. Zach''s Grandparents found leaving Eph with a choice. Eldritch discovers the "White" has an unexpected price at Eichhorst''s delight.', 2, 12, '27 Sep. 2015'),
