(12367, 'tt0539374', '168', 'I''ve Got You Under My Skin', 'MV5BMTQ2MjM4NjE5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjQwOTEzMjE@', 'Phoebe can''t resist a peek into the future. She and her sisters learn their first lesson in witchcraft - deadly demons can come in any kind of package, including gorgeous male photographers.', 1, 3, '14 Oct. 1998'),
