(12378, 'tt0539364', '168', 'From Fear to Eternity', 'MV5BMTAwMjQ3ODU4OTZeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDIzMDkxMzIx', 'Every 1,300 years, a unique demon appears that feeds on the fears of witches. This time it is targeting the Halliwell sisters and they receive aid from their Wicca ancestors just as they are close to their own fearful deaths.', 1, 14, '10 Feb. 1999'),
