(12409, 'tt0539331', '168', 'Be Careful What You Witch For', 'MV5BODI4MjY2MTA0Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzg5ODEzMjE@', 'A Genie, employed by a Dragon Warlock to steal the Halliwells'' powers, offers to grant each sister one wish for whatever they most desire.', 2, 22, '18 May 2000'),
