(12415, 'tt0539411', '168', 'Primrose Empath', 'MV5BMTQ2MjIzMzc4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjkwOTEzMjE@', 'Phoebe and Piper are on a mission to save Prue after a spell for an innocent horribly backfires and Prue is given the unwanted gift of feeling all the pain in the world. The cacophony of human emotion will most certainly crush her.', 3, 6, '9 Nov. 2000'),
(12416, 'tt0539409', '168', 'Power Outage', 'MV5BMjIxOTMxNDY5NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzkwOTEzMjE@', 'Cole uses petty anger between Prue, Phoebe, and Piper to break their bond and destroy the very foundation of their powers, leaving the sisters defenseless against demonic attack.', 3, 7, '16 Nov. 2000'),
