(12420, 'tt0539334', '168', 'Blinded by the Whitelighter', 'MV5BMTcyNjY4ODUyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY5ODEzMjE@', 'The sisters must stop a warlock from executing his plan to steal specific powers from witches in his attempt to kill every whitelighter in the world. Meanwhile, the girls get a new whitelighter named Natalie.', 3, 11, '25 Jan. 2001'),
(12421, 'tt0539485', '168', 'Wrestling with Demons', 'MV5BMjM4NTgzOTE4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTI3ODEzMjE@', 'When Prue discovers that one of her ex-boyfriends is being led down the path to becoming a demon, she, Piper and Phoebe risk their lives in an underworld wrestling ring to save his soul.', 3, 12, '1 Feb. 2001'),
