(12888, 'tt2772856', '179', 'Catherine', 'MV5BMjA4MTEwNTM3MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDAwNDE1MDE@', 'William and Libby experience personal tragedy. Masters decides to pair Austin with a stranger. Virginia struggles with her parenting due to her long hours. Ethan''s relationship with Vivian takes the next step, whether he likes it or not.', 1, 5, '27 Oct. 2013'),
